%2C%20really%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20told%20Biden%20in%20the%20Oval%20Ofice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESitting%20with%20Biden%20beneath%20portraits%20of%20former%20presidents%20George%20Washington%20and%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20and%20reading%20prepared%20remarks%20from%20cards%2C%20Zelensky%20also%20thanked%20Congress%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bbig%2C%20huge%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20hailed%20the%20%26quot%3Benormous%20bravery%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20people%20as%20they%20fight%20back%20Russia's%20invasion%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20American%20people%20are%20determined%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20we%20do%20all%20we%20can%20to%20ensure%20the%20world%20stands%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20supporting%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%2C%20one%20that%20respects%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20his%20second%20wartime%20visit%20to%20Washington%2C%20Zelensky%20faced%20a%20far%20trickier%20political%20landscape%20than%20when%20he%20arrived%20to%20a%20hero's%20welcome%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20White%20House%20announced%20it%20would%20give%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20air%20defense%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20was%20no%20deal%20to%20provide%20the%20long-range%20missiles%20that%20Zelensky%20covets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Congress%2C%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20leaders%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20bitter%20spending%20battle%20that%20could%20spark%20a%20US%20government%20shutdown%2C%20with%20a%20%2424%20billion%20aid%20package%20for%20Ukraine%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Lose%20the%20war'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hard-right%20faction%20dominating%20the%20Republican%20Party%20is%20increasingly%20adamant%20that%20the%20aid%20spigot%20should%20be%20turned%20off%2C%20with%20Congress%20having%20already%20approved%20%24100%20billion%20in%20aid%20to%20date%2C%20including%20%2443%20billion%20in%20weaponry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20leader%20arrived%20right%20after%20another%20wave%20of%20Russian%20missile%20strikes.%20The%20attacks%20--%20hitting%20cities%20across%20the%20country%20--%20killed%20at%20least%20three%20people%20in%20Kherson%20and%20wounded%20many%20in%20other%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Senate%20leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20a%20major%20supporter%20of%20Biden's%20pro-Ukraine%20policies%2C%20said%20Zelensky%20had%20told%20him%20%26quot%3Bif%20we%20don't%20get%20the%20aid%2C%20we%20will%20lose%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20bid%20to%20win%20over%20Washington%2C%20Zelensky%20went%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20where%20he%20laid%20a%20wreath%20at%20a%20memorial%20for%20victims%20of%20the%20September%2011%2C%202001%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20there%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20bipartisan%20support%20to%20continue%20funding%20Ukraine%26quot%3B%20despite%20the%20deep%20US%20political%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20blow%20to%20Zelensky%2C%20he%20said%20Biden%20had%20rejected%20for%20now%20a%20request%20for%20longer-range%20ATACMS%20missiles%20that%20can%20strike%20up%20to%20300%20kilometers%20(190%20miles)%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20Zelensky%20got%20a%20notably%20discreet%20welcome%20from%20the%20Republican%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20Kevin%20McCarthy%2C%20who%20is%20having%20trouble%20keeping%20a%20lid%20on%20internal%20party%20squabbling%20over%20US%20spending%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20Republicans%20say%20the%20money%20could%20be%20better%20spent%20on%20US%20border%20security%2C%20while%20there%20are%20also%20concerns%20about%20the%20pace%20of%20Kyiv's%20counteroffensive%20and%20that%20corruption%20in%20Ukraine%20means%20the%20money%20will%20go%20to%20wast