mily%20and%20its%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20plucked%20straight%20from%20reality%20and%20put%20onto%20the%20screen%20for%20HBO's%20hit%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20which%20of%20Murdoch's%20children%20would%20rise%20up%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Fox%20Corp.%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Fox%20News%2C%20and%20News%20Corp.%2C%20an%20empire%20that%20includes%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20New%20York%20Post%2C%20and%20the%20UK's%20The%20Times%2C%20among%20other%20assets.%20Some%20suspected%20that%2C%20like%20Logan%20Roy%2C%20Murdoch%20might%20never%20choose%20a%20successor%20at%20all%2C%20preferring%20to%20die%20on%20top%20rather%20than%20watch%20one%20of%20his%20kids%20take%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20now%20convinced%20of%20my%20own%20immortality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20beating%20prostate%20cancer%20over%20two%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrudence%2C%20Murdoch's%20only%20child%20with%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20only%20one%20of%20his%20children%20not%20directly%20competing%20for%20his%20business%20affections%2C%26quot%3B%20Murdoch%20biographer%20Michael%20Wolff%20wrote%20in%202008%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fnews%2F2008%2F12%2Fmurdoch200812%3FcurrentPage%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20other%20three%20adult%20children%20%E2%80%94%20Elisabeth%2C%20Lachlan%2C%20and%20James%20%E2%80%94%20spent%20much%20of%20their%20lives%20competing%20for%20the%20title%20of%20heir%20apparent%2C%20reportedly%20beginning%20their%20training%20in%20the%20family%20business%20as%20little%20kids%20around%20a%20newspaper%20at%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20friends%20of%20the%20Murdochs%20liked%20to%20say%2C%20Murdoch%20didn't%20raise%20children%3B%20he%20raised%20future%20media%20moguls%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2019%2F04%2F03%2Fmagazine%2Frupert-murdoch-fox-news-trump.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20journalists%20Jonathan%20Mahler%20and%20Jim%20Rutenberg%20wrote%20in%20a%202019%20investigation%20into%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElisabeth%2C%20the%20eldest%20of%20Murdoch's%20three%20children%20with%20his%20second%20wife%2C%20is%20often%20said%20to%20be%20the%20smartest%20of%20the%20siblings%2C%20though%2C%20as%20with%20Siobhan%20Roy%2C%20being%20a%20woman%20was%20never%20in%20her%20favor.%20She%20quit%20the%20family%20business%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20left%20Lachlan%20and%20James%2C%20who%20have%20passed%20the%20title%20of%20successor%20between%20the%20two%20of%20them%20over%20the%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20much%20of%20the%202000s%20and%202010s%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%20James%20would%20eventually%20take%20over%20the%20family%20business.%20Much%20like%20Kendall%20Roy%2C%20James%20was%20a%20quick%20study%20and%20the%20conventional%20choice%2C%20with%20the%20white%20button-downs%20and%20MBA-speak%20favored%20by%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJames%20is%20like%20his%20father%2C%20News%20Corp.%20people%20believe.%20Or%20at%20least%20he%20tries%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolff%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20may%20not%20be%20so%20much%20his%20father%20that%20he's%20emulating%20as%20some%20generic%20idea%20of%20the%20advanced%20business%20figure%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20News%20Corp.%20in%20his%20early%2020s%2C%20James%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20eventually%20becoming%20the%20CEO%20of%2021st%20Century%20Fox%20and%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20News%20Corp.%20He%20led%20the%20latter's%20UK%20division%20during%20the%20notorious%20phone-hacking%20scandal%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20mirrored%20Kendall's%20cruise%20debacle%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20also%20like%20Kendall%2C%20has%20an%20affinity%20for%20hip%20hop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Murdoch's%20favorite%20son%2C%20Lachlan%2C%20has%20been%20a%20Roman%20Roy-esque%20wild%20card%2C%20with%20the%20same%20right-wing%20politics%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BSuccession%26quot%3B%20character.%20While%20James%20was%20helping%20the%20family%20empire%20adapt%20to%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20Lachlan%20was%20in%20Australia%2C%20looking%20for%20his%20own%20kingdom%20after%20abruptly%20resigning%20from%20his%20position%20as%20the%20number%20three%20man%20at%20News%20Corp%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20boy%20who%20wouldn't%20be%20king%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnymag.com%2Fnymetro%2Fnews%2Fmedia%2Ffeatures%2F14302%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Magazine%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%20spelled%20out%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20world%20wrote%20Lachlan%20off%20too%20soon.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20was%20back%2C%20this%20time%20as%20co-chairman%20of%20both%20of%20the%20family's%20conglomerates.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20he%20was%20named%20executive%20chairman%20of%2021st%20Century%20Fox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20big%20slap%20in%20the%20face%26quot%3B%20for%20James%2C%20a%20source%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F04%2Frupert-murdoch-cover-story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gabriel%20Sherman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20succession%20saga%20seemed%20all%20but%20officially%20over%3A%20Lachlan%20was%20running%20what%20was%20left%20of%20Fox%20following%20Disney's%20%2471.3%20billion%20acquisition%20of%20most%20of%20its%20assets%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffox-news-james-murdoch-says-fathers-media-empire-obscures-facts-2020-10%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EJames%2C%20an%20outspoken%20Democrat%2C%20stepped%20down%20from%20News%20Corp.'s%3C%2Fa%3E%20board%2C%20citing%20%26quot%3Bdisagreements%20over%20certain%20editorial%20content%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20other%20strategic%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20great%20news%20organizations%2C%20the%20mission%20really%20should%20be%20to%20introduce%20fact%20to%20disperse%20doubt%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20sow%20doubt%2C%20to%20obscure%20fact%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F10%2F10%2Fstyle%2Fjames-murdoch-maureen-dowd.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20months%20later.%20(In%20the%20same%20interview%2C%20he%20insisted%20he%20didn't%20watch%20%26quot%3BSuccession.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20with%20any%20melodramatic%20narrative%2C%20chatter%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20the%20family%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffox-ceo-lachlan-murdoch-profile-interview-2021-5%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20that%20James%20was%20%26quot%3Brunning%20a%20whisper%20campaign%20that%20Lachlan%20is%20not%20good%20at%20his%20job%20and%20that%20he%20doesn't%20deserve%20it.%26quot%3B%20That%20same%20year%2C%20James%20skipped%20his%20dad's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frupert-murdoch-90th-birthday-party-guest-list-2021-10%5C%22%3E90th%20birthday%20party%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20this%20May%2C%20James%20and%20Lachlan%20weren't%20speaking%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F04%2Frupert-murdoch-cover-story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESherman%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20sources%20told%20him%20that%20James%20is%20thinking%20up%20ways%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20company%20once%20his%20father%20is%20%E2%80%94%20truly%20%E2%80%94%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20as%20with%20any%20good%20saga%2C%20there%20is%20often%20a%20sequel.%3C%2Fp%3