id%20Standoff%2C%20US%20Says%20%26quot%3BIn%20Constant%20Touch%20With%20Canada%20And%20India%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20on%20Thursday%20said%20he%20will%20not%20be%20going%20into%20the%20substance%20of%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20US%20is%20consulting%20with%20Ottawa%20closely%20and%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20as%20well.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20Sullivan%20said%20the%20US%20supports%20the%20efforts%20that%20are%20being%20taken%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20perpetrators%20held%20to%20account.%20He%20rejected%20the%20reports%20that%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20gap%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20ongoing%20fierce%20diplomatic%20standoff%2C%20Sullivan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20heard%20from%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20publicly%20about%20the%20allegations.%20We%20went%20out%20publicly%20ourselves%20and%20expressed%20our%20deep%20concern%20about%20them.%20Our%20support%20for%20a%20law%20enforcement%20process%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20held%20accountable.%20Not%20going%20to%20get%20into%20the%20substance%20of%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations%2C%20but%20we%20are%20in%20constant%20contact%20with%20our%20Canadian%20counterparts.%20We%20are%20consulting%20with%20them%20closely.%20We%20support%20the%20efforts%20that%20they%20are%20undertaking%20in%20this%20investigation%2C%20and%20we%20have%20also%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20will%20leave%20it%20at%20that%20for%20today.%20Only%20to%20say%20that%20I%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20press%20some%20efforts%20to%20try%20to%20drive%20a%20wedge%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Canada%20on%20this%20issue.%20And%20I%20firmly%20reject%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20is%20a%20wedge%20between%20the%20US%20And%20Canada.%20We%20have%20deep%20concerns%20about%20the%20allegations%20and%20we%20would%20like%20to%20see%20this%20investigation%20carried%20forward%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20held%20to%20account.%3Cbr%3E%20That%20is%20what%20the%20United%20States%20has%20stood%20for%20from%20the%20moment%20this%20emerged%20in%20public%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20stand%20for%20that%20until%20this%20fully%20plays%20its%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20Canadian%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20assassination%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20The%20chief%20of%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Sikh%20extremist%20organisation%20banned%20by%20India%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdesignated%20terrorist%26quot%3B%2C%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20targeted%20shooting%20at%20British%20Columbia%20in%20Canada's%20Surrey%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20the%20allegations%2C%20terming%20them%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20and%20rejected%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20their%20Parliament%2C%20as%20also%20the%20statement%20by%20their%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BAllegations%20of%20Government%20of%20India's%20involvement%20in%20any%20act%20of%20violence%20in%20Canada%20are%20absurd%20and%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20added%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilar%20allegations%20were%20made%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20were%20completely%20rejected.%20We%20are%20a%20democratic%20polity%20with%20a%20strong%20commitment%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3Cbr%3E%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20reciprocal%20move%20to%20Canada%20expelling%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%20in%20light%20of%20the%20claim%20of%20New%20Delhi's%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20wanted%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%20The%20MEA%20said%20the%20Canadian%20diplomat%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20India%20within%20the%20next%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Canada%20to%20India%20was%20summoned%20today%20and%20informed%20about%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20expel%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20based%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20stated%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concerned%20diplomat%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20leave%20India%20within%20the%20next%20five%20days.%20The%20decision%20reflects%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20growing%20concern%20at%20the%20interference%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20our%20internal%20matters%20and%20their%20involvement%20in%20anti-India%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695324600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fgbdue9no_-jake-sullivan-reuters_625x300_06_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famid-diplomatic-standoff-us-says-in-constant-touch-with-canada-and-india-4412379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20on%20Thursday%20said%20he%20will%20not%20be%20going%20into%20the%20substance%20of%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations.%22%2C%22author%22%