ecession%20gauge%20is%20likely%20correct%2C%20according%20to%20Campbell%20Harvey.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Duke%20professor%20popularized%20the%203-10%20Treasury%20spread%20as%20a%20recession%20indicator%20in%201995.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20gauge%20has%20never%20flashed%20a%20false%20positive%20-%20and%20it's%20likely%20saying%20the%20Fed%20made%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%20Harvey%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inverted%20yield%20curve%20is%20still%20correctly%20signaling%20a%20recession%20even%20as%20optimism%20grows%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20is%20making%20a%20major%20mistake%20in%20its%20war%20against%20inflation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20economist%20who%20popularized%20the%20bond%20market's%20notorious%20economic%20indicator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampbell%20Harvey%2C%20the%20Duke%20University%20finance%20professor%20who%20coined%20the%20inverted%20yield%20curve%20as%20an%20indicator%20of%20a%20coming%20downturn%20in%201995%2C%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20accuracy%20of%20his%20famed%20recession%20gauge%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-inflation-cpi-august-us-economy-fed-2023-9%3F_gl%3D1*smz72r*_ga*MjMxMzA1Mzg2LjE2NTY0NDQxNTU.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5NDYyNjQ1NC42MjUuMS4xNjk0NjMyMzU2LjUuMC4w%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20curve%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20difference%20between%20the%203-month%20and%2010-year%20Treasury%20yields%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FT10Y3M%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorrectly%20predicted%20every%20recession%20since%201968%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20market%20forecasters%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frecession-odds-economic-outlook-interest-inflation-jobs-data-soft-landing-2023-7%5C%22%3Ewarmed%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20soft%20landing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20closely%20watched%20recession%20gauge%20is%20still%20likely%20correct%2C%20Harvey%20said%2C%20even%20though%20a%20downturn%20hasn't%20yet%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20yield%20curve%20inversion%20typically%20lags%20behind%20the%20start%20of%20the%20recession%2C%20with%20the%20average%20wait%20time%20over%20the%20past%20four%20recessions%20being%2013%20months%20from%20the%20start%20of%20the%20inversion.%20The%20curve%20officially%20inverted%20on%20October%2026%20last%20year%2C%20Fed%20data%20shows%2C%20meaning%20the%20recession%20signal%20is%20just%20a%20few%20days%20shy%20of%20the%2011-month%20milestone.%20If%20history%20is%20any%20guide%2C%20that%20would%20put%20the%20start%20date%20of%20a%20potential%20recession%20sometime%20in%20December%20or%20January%2C%20Harvey%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20the%20yield%20curve%20has%20flattened%20its%20inversion%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20that's%20typical%20behavior%20and%20such%20a%20flattening%20has%20preceded%20the%20last%20four%20recessions%2C%20Harvey%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indicator%20is%20eight%20out%20of%20eight%20when%20predicting%20recessions%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20have%20any%20false%20signals.%20So%20it's%20way%20too%20early%20to%20say%20this%20is%20a%20false%20signal.%20Maybe%20it%20does%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20false%20signal%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20say%20it's%20a%20false%20signal%20when%20you're%20not%20even%20at%20the%20average%2C%26quot%3B%20Harvey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20similar%20recession%20indicators%20have%20been%20known%20to%20flash%20false%20positives.%20The%20other%20famous%20spread%2C%20between%20the%202-year%20and%2010-year%20Treasury%20notes%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frecession-warning-economic-outlook-inverted-yield-curve-fed-rate-hike-2023-1%5C%22%3Ecorrectly%20predicted%20e