ns%20to%20140%20crore%20Indians.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20I%20thank%20all%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20who%20voted%20for%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam.%20Such%20unanimous%20support%20is%20indeed%20gladdening.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20With%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1704904798401872144%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20quota%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20which%2C%20under%20Constitution's%20Article%2082%2C%20can%20be%20conducted%20after%202026%2C%20which%20pushes%20the%20implementation%20to%202029%20or%20beyond.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20said%20that%20the%20census%20and%20delimitation%20will%20begin%20after%20next%20year's%20general%20election%2C%20implementing%20quota%20sooner%20may%20call%20for%20a%20constitutional%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20put%20on%20record%20two%20key%20demands%20--%20immediate%20implementation%20of%20quota%20and%20a%20sub-category%20of%20reservation%20for%20women%20from%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695322380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9ssrlo2g_narendra-modi-women-mps-_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-womens-bill-passes-through-rajya-sabha-a-vote-of-thanks-for-pm-4412338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Close%20to%20the%20midnight%20hour%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20seen%20posing%20for%20photos%20with%20hordes%20of%20laughing%2C%20chattering%20women%20MPs%20at%20the%20new%20building.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.