0...there%20is%20something%20of%20utmost%20foundational%20importance%20in%20a%20country's%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20a%20world%20where%20international%20rules-based%20order%20matters...we%20have%20rigorous%20and%20independent%20judges%20and%20robust%20processes..%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20took%20questions%20about%20Canada's%20tensions%20with%20India%2C%20after%20both%20countries%20took%20a%20series%20of%20diplomatic%20steps%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20call%20upon%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20take%20seriously%20this%20matter%20and%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20shed%20full%20transparency%20and%20ensure%20accountability%20and%20justice%20in%20this%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20country%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20the%20work%20necessary%20to%20keep%20Canadians%20safe%20and%20to%20uphold%20our%20values%20and%20the%20international%20rules-based%20order.%20That's%20our%20focus%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20further%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20standing%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20or%20highlighting%20how%20unacceptable%20it%20would%20be%20for%20any%20country%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20citizen%20on%20its%20own%20soil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20important%20that%20as%20a%20country%20with%20a%20strong%2C%20independent%20justice%20system%20...%20we%20allow%20those%20justice%20processes%20to%20unfold%20themselves%20with%20the%20utmost%20integrity.%20but%20I%20assure%20this%20decision%20to%20share%20these%20allegations%20on%20the%20floor%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20on%20Monday%20morning%20was%20not%20made%20lightly%20and%20was%20done%20with%20utmost%20seriousness%2C%26quot%3B%20Canada's%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20also%20highlighted%20the%20conversation%20he%20had%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20direct%20and%20frank%20conversation%2C%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(Modi)%2C%20in%20which%20I%20shared%20my%20concerns%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms...%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20the%20Indian%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20in%20its%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%20by%20Canada%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%20these%20allegations%20were%20raised%20by%20Canadian%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau%20with%20PM%20(Modi)%20and%20PM%20rejected%20them.%26quot%3B%20The%20MEA%20said%20that%20allegations%20were%20raised%20by%20Justin%20Trudeau%20when%20he%20was%20in%20India%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Summit%20and%20that%20PM%20Modi%20had%20rejected%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20Canada%20has%20not%20shared%20any%20specific%20information%20regarding%20the%20allegations%20and%20that%20India%20is%20asking%20Canada%20to%20take%20action%20against%20those%20facing%20charges%20related%20to%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20any%20specific%20information%20that%20is%20provided%20to%20us%2C%20but%20so%20far%20we%20have%20received%20no%20specific%20information%20from%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Bagchi%20said%20on%20Thursday%20answering%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India's%20visa%20processing%20centre%20in%20Canada%20on%20Thursday%20suspended%20its%20services%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20Indian%20students%20in%20Canada%20were%20advised%20to%20avoid%20traveling%20to%20regions%20and%20potential%20venues%20in%20Canada%20that%20have%20seen%20growing%20anti-India%20activities%2C%20according%20to%20a%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20students%20in