er%20repayment%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they%20qualify%20for%20debt%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20New%20Jersey%20Sen.%20Bob%20Menendez%20led%20five%20of%20his%20Democratic%20colleagues%2C%20including%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20in%20sending%20a%20letter%20to%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20regarding%20the%20treatment%20of%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program.%20PSLF%20is%20intended%20to%20forgive%20student%20loans%20of%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%20ten%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments%2C%20and%20borrowers%20within%20that%20program%C2%A0have%20their%20loans%20managed%20by%20student-loan%20company%20MOHELA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter%20first%20viewed%20by%20Insider%20that%20borrowers%20serviced%20by%20MOHELA%20have%20reported%20a%20range%20of%20concerns%20with%20the%20company%2C%20including%20long%20wait%20times%20to%20contact%20customer%20service%2C%20issues%20receiving%20credit%20for%20the%20qualifying%20payments%20they've%20made%20toward%20PSLF%2C%20and%20delays%20in%20getting%C2%A0refunds%20for%20borrowers%20who%20have%20received%20forgiveness%20through%20PSLF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20restart%20of%20repayments%2C%20these%20issues%20are%20likely%20to%20worsen%20for%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Department%20explores%20ways%20to%20ensure%20that%20borrowers%20are%20held%20harmless%20with%20the%20restart%20of%20repayments%2C%20it%20is%20vital%20that%20you%20not%20overlook%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20continued.%20%26quot%3BBorrowers%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20have%20their%20debt%20cancelled%20under%20the%20PSLF%20program%20should%20not%20be%20forced%20back%20into%20repayment%20due%20solely%20to%20MOHELA's%20processing%20delays%2C%20which%20cause%20difficult%20financial%20situations%20for%20so%20many