iously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20they%20hurdles%20they've%20encountered%20when%20attempting%20to%20get%20a%20status%20update%20on%20their%20PSLF%20applications.%20One%20borrower%20said%20he%20simply%20wanted%20to%20confirm%20the%20payments%20he%20had%20made%20qualified%20for%20the%20program.%20But%20instead%2C%20he%20spent%20hours%20on%20hold%20and%20never%20got%20an%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20time%20I%20tried%20to%20call%20was%20a%20144%20minute%20estimated%20wait%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-cant-reach-company-mohela-pslf-debt-relief-2022-10%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20second%20time%20I%20called%20was%20a%20149%20minute%20wait.%20And%20then%20most%20recently%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20call%20and%20it%20was%2050%20minutes.%20And%20each%20of%20these%20times%20I%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20wait.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20quicker%20call.%20And%20one%20time%20I%20stayed%20on%20the%20call%20for%20nearly%20three%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20MOHELA%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-website-call-center-shut-down-borrowers-payments-2023-8%5C%22%3Enot%20the%20only%20servicer%20that's%20been%20hit%20with%20customer%20service%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20borrowers%20in%20PSLF%20are%20relying%20on%20it%20to%20properly%20administer%20debt%20relief%20once%20they%20qualify%20and%20process%20their%20paperwork%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%20Scott%20Buchanan%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Student%20Loan%20Servicing%20Alliance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20represents%20federal%20loan%20servicers%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-facing-perfect-storm-repayment-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20delays%20come%20down%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20the%20Education%20Department%20can%20offer%20due%20to%20limited%20congressional%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-eligible-debt-cancellation-forced-into-repayment-pslf-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695321378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650c86b412dc4f001a17954a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-eligible-debt-cancellation-forced-into-repayment-pslf-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sens.%20Bob%20Menendez%20and%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20were%20among%20lawmakers%20concerned%20with%20student-loan%20company%20MOHELA's%20delays%20in%20processing%20PSLF%20for%20borrowers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-eligible-debt-cancellation-forced-into-repayment-pslf-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Timing%20of%20King's%20climate%20remarks%20in%20France%20felt%20awkward%20-%20as%20UK%20government%20delays%20targets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695321360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-king-charles-french-senate_6293191.jpg%3F20230921200358%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftiming-of-kings-climate-remarks-in-france-felt-awkward-as-uk-government-delays-targets-12966635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20busy%20days%2C%20but%20job%20done%20for%20the%20King%20and%20Queen%20in%20Paris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftiming-of-kings-climate-remarks-in-france-felt-awkward-as-uk-government-delays-targets-12966635%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%