ot%20find%20one%20woman%20in%2016%20NDA%20states%20for%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20at%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20debate.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EFormer%20Union%20minister%20Kapil%20Sibal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20who%20will%20come%20to%20power%2C%20but%20they%20must%20make%20a%20statement%20that%20if%20they%20don't%20complete%20the%20process%20by%202029%2C%20they%20will%20resign%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20home%20minister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUnion%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20in%20an%20intervention%20during%20the%20debate%2C%20said%20the%20Centre%20convened%20the%20special%20session%20to%20give%20a%20good%20start%20to%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20through%20the%20historic%20bill.%20The%20BJP%20does%20not%20play%20politics%20in%20matters%20related%20to%20women%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20insists%20that%20the%20Census%20and%20delimitation%20are%20meant%20to%20ensure%20exactitude%20and%20transparency.%20%26quot%3BDelimitation%20Commission%20is%20an%20important%20body%20for%20poll%20process%20in%20the%20country.%20If%20we%20are%20reserving%20one-third%20seats...%20who%20will%20do%20it%3F%20If%20we%20do%20it%2C%20you%20(the%20Opposition)%20will%20question%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20slammed%20the%20Congress%20today%20during%20the%20debate%20for%20demanding%20OBC%20quota%20within%20the%20reservation%20for%20women%20lawmakers%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20that%20gave%20the%20country%20its%20first%20OBC%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOnce%20implemented%2C%20the%20number%20of%20women%20members%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20increase%20from%20the%20current%2082%20to%20181.%20Besides%2C%2033%20per%20cent%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20state%20assemblies%20also.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169532118