OpenAI%20claiming%20copyright%20infringement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20OpenAI%20is%20using%20the%20works%20of%20authors%20to%20train%20ChatGPT%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20follows%20a%20series%20of%20lawsuits%20writers%20launched%20against%20OpenAI%20over%20similar%20accusations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWriters%20have%20launched%20yet%20another%20lawsuit%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Authors%20Guild%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20represents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauthorsguild.org%2Fnews%2Fag-and-authors-file-class-action-suit-against-openai%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520the%2520oldest%2520and%2520largest%2Chas%2520expertise%2520in%2520copyright%2520law.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%2014%2C000%20U.S.%20authors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prominent%20writers%20within%20it%20sued%20OpenAI%20in%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20over%20allegations%20that%20the%20ChatGPT-maker%20trained%20its%20large%20language%20AI%20models%20on%20the%20works%20of%20authors%20like%20George%20R.R.%20Martin%2C%20the%20novelist%20behind%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BA%20Game%20of%20Thrones%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20John%20Grisham%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20nonconsensual%20training%2C%20the%20conversational%20AI%20chatbot%20would%20%26quot%3Ballow%20anyone%20to%20generate%26quot%3B%20texts%20that%20the%20publishers%20would%20%26quot%3Botherwise%20pay%20writers%20to%20create%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bspit%20out%20derivative%20works%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20summaries%20or%20paraphrases%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.606655%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.606655.1.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%