lice%20officer%20who%20was%20investigating%20him.%20The%20officer%20was%20arrested%20on%20multiple%20charges%20including%20corruption.%20He%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20magistrate%20in%20Srinagar%20who%20sent%20him%20to%20police%20custody%20for%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20phone%20analysis%20of%20the%20terror%20accused%20arrested%20in%20July%20has%20revealed%20that%20Aadil%20Mushtaq%20was%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20him.%20He%20allegedly%20guided%20him%20on%20how%20to%20circumvent%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20officer%2C%20Aadil%20Mushtaq%20used%20to%20talk%20and%20chat%20with%20the%20accused%20on%20telegram%20app.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20at%20least%2040%20calls%20between%20the%20terror%20accused%20and%20the%20Deputy%20Superintendent.%20He%20was%20guiding%20him%20how%20to%20evade%20arrest%20and%20get%20legal%20aid%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20officer%20supervising%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20police%20have%20made%20a%20watertight%20case%20against%20the%20officer%20based%20on%20technical%20evidence%20and%20money%20trail.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20clinching%20evidences%20on%20how%20he%20was%20helping%20the%20terror%20accused.%20Aadil%20even%20tried%20to%20implicate%20a%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20investigating%20the%20case%20of%20terror%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20had%20even%20drafted%20a%20false%20complaint%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20terror%20accused%20to%20implicate%20the%20investigation%20officer%20in%20a%20terror%20funding%20case%2C%20in%20which%20three%20accused%20were%20arrested%20in%20February%20and%20one%20was%20on%20the%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20say%20Aadil%20Mushtaq%20had%20taken%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20the%20accused.%20He%20was%20also%20in%20close%20touch%20with%20Muzamil%20Zahoor%2C%20who%20had%20opened%20a%20bank%20account%20on%20forged%20documents%