-10%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0ahead%20of%20the%202020%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-instagram-post-largest-voter-registration-day-since-2020-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695319015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650c7ec812dc4f001a17934e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-instagram-post-largest-voter-registration-day-since-2020-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift%2C%20who%20was%20notably%20silent%20about%20politics%20until%202018%2C%20urged%20her%20followers%20to%20register%20to%20vote%20in%20an%20Instagram%20story%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rcohen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Cohen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A86%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-instagram-post-largest-voter-registration-day-since-2020-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sperm%20Bank%20In%20China%20Is%20Holding%20A%20Contest%20To%20Find%20The%20Best%20Quality%20Of%20Semen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sperm%20bank%20in%20China%20is%20holding%20a%20unique%20contest%20for%20university%20students%20to%20find%20who%20has%20the%20best%20quality%20of%20semen%2C%20amid%20the%20country's%20falling%20birth%20rates.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Fsocial-welfare%2Farticle%2F3234560%2Fstrongest-swimmers-wanted-china-semen-bank-lures-university-students-donate-cash-and-contest-find%3Futm_source%3DNewswav%26utm_medium%3DWebsite%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%2C%20students%20will%20also%20be%20offered%20cash%C2%A0to%20donate%20their%20semen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EThe%20contest%20organised%20by%20Henan%20Provincial%20Human%20Sperm%20Bank%20aims%20to%20find%20both%20the%20man%20with%20the%20highest%20sperm%20count%20and%20the%20most%20vigorous%20sperm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Fchina-sperm-bank-runs-competition-for-high-quality-university-student-samples%5C%22%3EThe%20Straits%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20participants%20will%20also%20have%2050%20days%20to%20make%20up%20to%2020%20donations%20and%20will%20be%20paid%20up%20to%206%2C100%20yuan%20(69%2C357)%20each%20for%20their%20efforts.%20They%20will%20also%20be%20compensated%20for%20expenses%20incurred%2C%20including%20transport%20costs%20and%20the%20number%20of%20donations%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EParticipants%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%C2%A020-45%20and%20be%20at%20least%201.65m%20tall.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20must%20not%20be%20smokers%2C%20alcoholics%2C%20habitual%20drug%20users%2C%20or%20have%20same-sex%20or%20promiscuous%20sexual%20histories.%20Semen%20samples%20will%20be%20evaluated%20on%20at%20least%20four%20criteria--%20sperm%20concentration%2C%20volume%2C%20structure%2C%20and%20motility%2C%20or%20how%20fast%20their%20sperm%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EThe%20contest%2C%20announced%20on%20September%2010%2C%20comes%20as%20the%20country%20grapples%20with%20reports%20of%C2%A0declining%20sperm%20counts%20among%20men%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20low%20birth%20rate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3E''Due%20to%20environmental%20pollution%20and%20work%20pressure%2C%20the%20overall%20sperm%20quality%20has%20deteriorated.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20infertility%20in%20a%20number%20of%20married%20couples%2C%20bringing%20disharmony%20to%20their%20families%20and%20society.%20Like%20blood%2C%20sperm%20donation%20is%20a%20humanitarian%20activity.%20It%20can%20bring%20good%20news%20to%20infertile%20couples.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20call%20on%20university%20students%20to%20donate%20sperm%20to%20make%20a%20contribution%20to%20society%2C''%20the%20Henan%20sperm%20bank%20said%20on%20Weibo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3ENotably%2C%20China%20scrapped%20its%20decades-long%20one-child%20policy%20in%202015%2C%20allowing%20all%20couples%20to%20have%20two%20children.%20Authorities%20raised%20the%20limit%20to%20three%20in%202021%2C%20but%20even%20during%20stay-at-home%20COVID%20times%2C%20couples%20were%20reluctant%20to%20have%20babies.%20China%20is%20now%20desperately%20trying%20to%20boost%20its%20declining%20number%20of%20new%20births%20after%20the%20country's%20fertility%20rate%20dropped%20to%20a%20record%20low%20of%201.09%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EConcerned%20about%20this%20and%20its%20rapidly%20ageing%20population%2C%20Beijing%20is%20trying%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-chinas-birth-rate-falls-college-students-given-a-week-off-to-fall-in-love-report-3913007%5C%22%3Eslew%20of%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lift%20the%20birth%20rate.%20However%2C%20young%20people%20cite%20high%20childcare%20and%20education%20costs%2C%20low%20incomes%2C%20a%20feeble%20social%20safety%20net%2C%20and%20gender%20inequalities%20as%20discouraging%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695318960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fh5u0a4jg_china-students_625x300_21_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-students-are-being-offered-cash-to-donate-semen-in-this-unique-contest-4412158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20contest%20organised%20by%20Henan%20Provincial%20Human%20Sperm%20Bank%20aims%20to%20find%20both%20the%20man%20with%20the%20highest%20sperm%20count%20and%20the%20most%20vigorous%20spe