within%20two%20days%20after%20June%201%2C%20Kuki%20students%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20hill%20areas%20have%20opted%20for%20admission%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Kannur%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20information%20received%20from%20the%20Kuki%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%20(KSO)%2C%20hundreds%20of%20students%20who%20were%20pursuing%20undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%2C%20and%20PhD%20degrees%20in%20Imphal%20are%20now%20seeking%20help%20from%20universities%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoulungmon%20Haokip%2C%20a%20student%20at%20LMS%20Law%20College%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20at%20least%2030%20students%20from%20Manipur%20University%20and%20Dhanamanjuri%20University%20have%20gained%20admission%20at%20Kannur%20University%20because%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20access%20their%20universities%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Goulongmon%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20passed%20entrance%20exams%20to%20secure%20admissions%20in%20universities%20in%20Imphal%2C%20but%20we%20never%20expected%20it%20would%20end%20up%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20think%20the%20violence%20should%20stop%2C%20and%20both%20communities%20should%20start%20living%20together%20peacefully%20so%20that%20students%E2%80%99%20lives%20can%20return%20to%20normal%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeace%20is%20a%20distant%20solution.%20Even%20if%20things%20settle%20down%20and%20return%20to%20normal%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20trust%20issues%20from%20both%20sides.%20The%20divide%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%20has%20deepened%20too%20much%3B%20now%20the%20only%20solution%20is%20separation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goulungmon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20KSO%20wrote%20to%20multiple%20universities%20and%20chief%20ministers%20to%20help%20Kuki%20students%20continue%20their%20studies%20in%20their%20respective%20state%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20sent%20letters%20to%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20We%20have%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20multiple%20universities%20in%20different%20states.%20Not%20only%20has%20Kannur%20University%20decided%20to%20assist%20us%2C%20but%20Delhi%20University%20is%20also%20willing%20to%20accommodate%20PhD%20students%20from%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mimin%20Haokip%2C%20the%20information%20and%20publicity%20secretary%20of%20the%20KSO%20general%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20KSO%20has%20submitted%20a%20list%20of%20students%20willing%20to%20enrol%20in%20the%20PhD%20programme%20at%20Delhi%20University.%20They%20are%20still%20awaiting%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20KSO%E2%80%99s%20education%20secretary%2C%20Thangmoi%2C%20and%20asked%20if%20the%20KSO%20had%20attempted%20to%20contact%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20for%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHome%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20have%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20Unless%20a%20separate%20administration%20is%20implemented%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20trust%20in%20the%20home%20minister%20and%20chief%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thangmoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20they%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20universities%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20KSO%20said%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%2C%20as%20they%20feel%20Imphal%20is%20no%20more%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20NIT%20Manipur%2C%20where%2050%20students%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20were%20demanding%20online%20classes.%20They%20raised%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20dean%2C%20L.%20Herojit%20Singh%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20students%20at%20NIT%20Manipur%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20multiple%20complaints%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20they%20arranged%20a%20few%20days%20of%20make-up%20online%20classes%20for%20us%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20continued%20with%20offline%20classes%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months%20before%20the%20examinations%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Paul%2C%20an%20M.Tech%20engineering%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20student%2C%20Zemin%2C%20who%20is%20pursuing%20a%20B.Tech%20degree%20at%20NIT%20Manipur%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20one%20teacher%20conducts%20online%20classes%20for%20us%3B%20the%20rest%20send%20us%20a%20few%20notes%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20before%20the%20examinations%2C%20and%20some%20we%20obtain%20from%20our%20friends%20at%20the%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20May%203%2C%20violence%20has%20affected%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20and%20thousands%20are%20now%20in%20relief%20camps%20as%20their%20houses%20got%20burnt%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20From%20schools%20to%20farming%20and%20businesses%2C%20everything%20has%20got%20affected%20by%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20June%201%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20made%20several%20promises%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%20One%20such%20promise%20was%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3Eformulate%20a%20plan%20for%20online%2