%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20initially%20started%20the%20orchid%20farm%2C%20he%20had%20procured%2015%20boxes%20of%20bees%20and%20colonies%20as%20well.%20This%20came%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20each.%20Later%2C%20he%20added%2025%20more%20colonies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20543px)%20100vw%2C%20543px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-briefing-interns-1695305568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Colonel%20Mohanty%20briefing%20interns%20at%20his%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-briefing-interns-1695305568.jpg%20543w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-briefing-interns-1695305568-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-briefing-interns-1695305568-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-briefing-interns-1695305568-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330568%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22285%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EColonel%20Mohanty%20briefing%20interns%20at%20his%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20honey%20from%20the%20first%20batch%20sells%20at%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20litre%2C%20bringing%20in%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%20Both%20these%20practices%20have%20immensely%20benefited%20each%20other%2C%20explains%20Sujan.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20apiculture%20has%20helped%20boost%20the%20orchid%20production%20by%2020%20percent%20through%20pollination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20teach%20farmers%20and%20interns%20at%20OUAT%20and%20at%20the%20Siksa%20%E2%80%98O%E2%80%99%20Anusandhan%20orchid%20farming%20and%20apicultu