nly%20two%20people%20have%20used%20spoons%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20so%20far%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20enjoy%20exploring%20and%20relishing%20the%20new%20food%20using%20their%20hands.%20Our%20authentic%20Kerala%20cuisine%20is%20very%20well%20received%20by%20the%20locals%20in%20Chicago%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Margaret.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStreet%20food%20stall%20to%20USA%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20restaurant%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMargaret%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20agricultural%20town%20in%20California.%20Before%20starting%20Thattu%2C%20she%20worked%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20for%2013%20years%20in%20several%20marketing%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20analytics%20companies.%20Being%20a%20foodie%2C%20she%20honed%20her%20culinary%20skills%20at%20a%20Korean%20restaurant%20where%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20prep%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20here%2C%20I%20learnt%20how%20to%20prepare%20menus%20and%20set%20up%20a%20restaurant%20business.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20developed%20a%20fondness%20for%20the%20cuisine%20of%20Kerala.%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20my%20own%20food%20business%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202019%2C%20Margaret%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20a%20street%20food%20stall%20to%20offer%20authentic%20Kerala%20dishes.%20By%20then%2C%20Vinod%20had%20also%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20joined%20his%20wife%20in%20running%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMargaret%20recalls%20how%20the%20American%20customers%20were%20baffled%20at%20first%20when%20she%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Eappams%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20often%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20making%20by%20the%20interested%20customers.%20%3Cem%3EAppams%3C%2Fem%3E%20look%20like%20pancakes%20but%20are%20cooked%20on%20only%20one%20side.%20It%20piqued%20their%20interests%20as%20they%20watched%20me%20cook%20it%20and%20wondered%20how%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20eat%20it.%20I%20would%20tell%20them