%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWomen%20Reservation%20to%20shift%20beyond%202034%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20If%20LS%20elections%20happen%20as%20per%20normal%20schedule%2C%20women%20reservation%20will%20come%20in%202039.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishikant%20Dubey%20links%20the%20delimitation%20for%20women%20reservation%20to%20Article%2081(3)%20and%2082.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fx3dDgwANNk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fx3dDgwANNk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gurdeep%20Singh%20Sappal%20(%40gurdeepsappal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgurdeepsappal%2Fstatus%2F1704380158264947080%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20do%20these%20Articles%20mean%3F%20Both%20these%20Articles%20assume%20significance%20as%20the%20current%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20census%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20delimitation%20commission%20that%20will%20redraw%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20It%20may%20also%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20decides%20to%20amend%20Article%2081.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%2081%20says%20that%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%20530%20members%20chosen%20by%20direct%20election%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%2020%20members%20chosen%20either%20through%20election%20or%20nomination%20from%20the%20Union%20Territories.%20Article%2081%20(3)%20says%20that%20these%20seats%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%201971%20decadal%20census.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20current%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20Article%2082%20becomes%20more%20important.%20Article%2082%20refers%20to%20the%20provision%20that%20reallocation%20of%20seats%20(delimitation)%20could%20be%20done%20only%20after%20every%20decennial%20census%20to%20ensure%20fair%20representation%20of%20all%20regions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20was%20constituted%20to%20reallocate%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20according%20to%20the%20first%20few%20rounds%20of%20census.%20However%2C%20the%2042nd%20amendment%2C%20passed%20in%201976%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20froze%20the%20delimitation%20of%20seats%20until%20the%202001%20census.%20In%202001%2C%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20passed%20the%2084th%20amendment%20that%20froze%20the%20number%20of%20constituencies%20till%202026%2C%20even%20as%20the%20census%20data%20was%20being%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20Article%2082%20virtually%20bars%20any%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20before%20the%202026%20census.%20The%20redrawing%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20can%20happen%20only%20after%20the%20census.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20freeze%20was%20introduced%20again%20to%20ensure%20that%20some%20regions%20which%20have%20fared%20better%20in%20controlling%20their%20population%20did%20not%20get%20left%20behind%20in%20terms%20of%20parliamentary%20representation.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20have%20performed%20well%20in%20restricting%20their%20birth%20rates%20but%20some%20north%20Indian%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20have%20not.%20In%20terms%20of%20the%20distribution%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20which%20is%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20population%20figures%2C%20the%20northern%20states%20could%20have%20a%20disproportionate%20advantage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20delimitation%20commission%20passed%20after%20the%202001%20census%20redrew%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20again%20ahead%20of%20the%202009%20general%20elections%20but%20did%20not%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20because%20of%20the%20freeze%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20Dubey%20said%20that%20Articles%2081%20and%2082%20prevented%20the%20Union%20government%20from%20implementing%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20meaning%20that%20a%20census%2C%20followed%20by%20another%20demilimitation%20exercise%2C%20had%20to%20happen%20before%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20could%20be%20introduced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20big%20question%2C%20however%2C%20is%20what%20is%20the%20likelihood%20of%20the%20quota%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%202029%20elections%3F%20Most%20experts%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20quota%20could%20be%20introduced%20by%202029.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20debate%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20could%20begin%20the%20census%20process%20immediately%20after%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20and%20that%20will%20allow%20it%20to%20implement%20it%20by%202029.%20However%2C%20experts%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20final%20report%20of%20the%202011%20Census%20was%20published%20only%20in%202013%2C%20after%20a%20two-year%20waiting%20period.%20The%202021%20census%20was%20postponed%20%E2%80%93%20initially%20because%20of%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20not%20given%20any%20definite%20timeline%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20take%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20word%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20initiate%20the%20census%20in%20mid-2024%2C%20the%20final%20report%20is%20expected%20only%20by%202026.%20The%20delimitation%20commission%20will%20then%20begin%20its%20work%20to%20reapportion%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20that%20should%20take%20at%20least%20another%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20introduction%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20is%20unlikely%20even%20in%20the%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20best-case%20scenario%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20sticks%20to%20its%20promise%20of%20initiating%20the%20census%20immediately%20after%20getting%20elected.%20Opposition%20leaders%20and%20political%20analysts%2C%20however%2C%20are%20more%20pessimistic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYogendra%20Yadav%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%2082%20(amended%20in%202001)%20virtually%20bars%20delimitation%20prior%20to%20the%20first%20census%20figures%20post%202026.%20That%20can%20only%20be%202031.%20Most%20observers%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20that%20(the)%20Delimitation%20Commission%20takes%203%20to%204%20years%20(last%20one%20took%205%20years)%20to%20give%20its%20final%20report.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20the%20coming%20delimitation%20can%20be%20very%20contentious%2C%20given%20the%20population%20ratio%20changes.%20So%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20report%20around%202037%20or%20so%2C%20that%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20in%202039.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMedia%20reports%20say%20Women's%20reservation%20would%20happen%20in%202029.%20This%20is%20misleading.%20Actually%20it%20may%20not%20happen%20till%202039.%3Cbr%3EMost%20media%20reports%20miss%20the%20real%20significance%20of%20the%20delimitation%20clause.%3Cbr%3EArticle%2082%20(amended%20in%202001)%20virtually%20bars%20delimitation%20prior%20to%20the%20first%20census%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20(%40_YogendraYadav)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_YogendraYadav%2Fstatus%2F1704350382653354011%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETMC%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20this%20government%20has%20brought%20here%20is%20not%20a%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Rescheduling%20Bill.%20Its%20agenda%20is%20delay%2C%20its%20agenda%20is%20not%20reservation.%20The%20constant%20dithering%20on%20when%20there%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Census%20and%20when%20there%20will%20be%20delimitation%20will%20mean%20that%20the%20reservation%20is%20indefinitely%20delayed.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20historic%20Bill%20as%20it%20is%20being%20touted.%20It%20is%20a%20sham.%20The%20question%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20requires%20action%2C%20not%20the%20legislatively%20mandated%20procrastination.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20means%2C%20in%20true%20BJP%20doublespeak%20style%2C%20we%20do%20not%20know%20if%2C%20and%20actually%20when%2C%20we%20will%20have%2033%20per%20cent%20women%20sitting%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20date%20of%20the%20next%20Census%20is%20entirely%20indeterminate.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20delimitation%20is%20doubly%20indeterminate.%20So%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20is%20dependent%20upon%20two%20totally%20indeterminate%20dates.%20Can%20there%20be%20a%20greater%20jumla%20%5Bempty%20promise%5D%3F%20Forget%202024%2C%20this%20may%20not%20even%20be%20possible%20in%202029%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmahua-moitra-calls-womens-quota-bill-sham-8948568%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20MPs%20from%20the%20southern%20states%2C%20like%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Kanimozhi%2C%20have%20also%20expressed%20fear%20that%20southern%20states%20may%20end%20up%20losing%20their%20number%20of%20seats%20after%202026%20(when%20the%20freeze%20ends)%20because%20of%20their%20lower%20birth%20rates%2C%20while%20northern%20states%2C%20despite%20performing%20poorly%20on%20that%20front%2C%20may%20add%20to%20their%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20situation%20may%20complicate%20the%20electoral%20matrix%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20political%20storm%2C%20delaying%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20even%20further.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20next%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20will%20be%20a%20complicated%20exercise%20as%20it%20will%20have%20to%20reapportion%20constituencies.%20The%20last%20such%20exercise%20took%20five%20years%20to%20complete%2C%20and%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20next%20exercise%2C%20a%20more%20complex%20one%2C%20may%20take%20longer.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20one%20is%20truly%20looking%20at%20the%202039%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20for%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20%E2%80%93%20as%20envisaged%20by%20the%20current%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20implemented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%2C%20however%2C%20another%20route%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20implement%20the%20reservation%20immediately.%20It%20could%20have%20chosen%20to%20delink%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20from%20the%20census%20and%20delimitation.%20A%20simpler%20Bill%20could%20have%20allowed%20all%20parties%20to%20ensure%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20within%20the%20current%20architecture%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20But%20since%20that%20has%20not%20happened%2C%20many%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20describing%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Bill%20as%20yet%20another%20%E2%80%9Celection%20%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695304858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21191937%2Flegislators.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%