0skips%20the%20unsettling%20questions.%20He%20is%20on%20the%20payroll%20of%20an%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20sent%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20names%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elist%20of%20journalists%20boycotted%20by%20the%20alliance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20what%E2%80%99s%20his%20take%20on%20his%20colleagues%20and%20their%20%E2%80%98journalism%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20organisation%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Findia-today-takes-rajdeep-sardesai-off-air-docks-months-salary-for-tweet-on-farmers-death%2F593990%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0him%20for%20two%20weeks%20and%20docked%20his%20salary%20for%20a%20false%20tweet%2C%20and%20sacked%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findia-today-angshukanta-chakraborty-dailyo%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20others%20for%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Faaj-tak-india-today-group-shyam-meera-singh-terminated-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20critical%20of%20the%20government%3Cspan%3E%2C%20did%20he%20point%20out%20to%20the%20management%20those%20numerous%20instances%20when%20his%20colleagues%20were%20found%20peddling%20hatred%20and%20falsehood%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20audience%20is%20waiting%20for%20him%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20my%20organisation%20is%20doing%20in%20the%20pretext%20of%20journalism%20is%20ominous%20for%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(Disclosure%3A%20I%20quit%20the%20organisation%20days%20after%20joining%20it.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPost-2014%20BJP%20has%20discredited%20the%20media%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShekhar%20Gupta%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fnational-interest%2Fopposition-can-choose-to-boycott-tv-anchors-but-a-list-paints-a-target-on-journalists-backs%2F1764216%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraises%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0a%20perfectly%20valid%20point%20that%20the%20list%20will%20not%20be%20the%20last%20one%2C%20and%20may%20set%20a%20dangerous%20precedent.%20But%20his%20other%20points%20negate%20his%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20requires%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enaivet%C3%A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20most%20brazen%20in%20its%20assault%20on%20press%20freedom%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20sophisticated%E2%80%9D.%20Its%20Union%20ministers%20popularised%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cpresstitute%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20the%20party%20went%20all%20out%20to%20discredit%20the%20media.%20The%20right-wing%20troll%20army%2C%20legitimised%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20who%20duly%20follows%20many%20of%20them%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20bullies%20and%20tarnishes%20journalists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-journalism-becomes-the-flagbearer-of-hate%5C%22%3EWhen%20Journalism%20Becomes%20the%20Flagbearer%20of%20Hate%2C%20Can%20the%20Resistance%20to%20It%20Be%20Anything%20but%20Political%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20previous%20governments%20had%20any%20issue%20with%20a%20news%20story%2C%20the%20topmost%20people%20tried%20to%20persuade%20the%20beat%20reporter.%20Now%2C%20a%20nondescript%20saffron%20flag%20holder%20directly%20calls%20and%20threatens%20editors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrue%2C%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20shining%20record%20about%20press%20freedom%2C%20but%20any%20journalist%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Union%20government%20or%20the%20BJP%20before%202014%20knows%20that%20other%20parties%20are%20several%20light%20years%20behind%20the%20current%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20several%20states%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20but%20its%20approach%20towards%20the%20media%20has%20drastically%20changed%20since%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202012%2C%20immediately%20after%20the%20killings%20of%2017%20Adivasis%20in%20CRPF%20firing%20in%20Bastar%2C%20a%20weekly%20placed%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20then-home%20minister%20with%20the%20corpses%20and%20asked%20on%20its%20cover%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20Chidambaram%20sleep%20well%20at%20night%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20has%20been%20burning%20for%20several%20months%2C%20with%20the%20death%20toll%20many%20times%20more%20than%20the%20Bastar%20incident.%20How%20many%20media%20houses%20can%20now%20give%20a%20similar%20headline%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20enabled%20the%20media%20to%20directly%20name%20the%20senior-most%20UPA%20leaders%3F%20With%20all%20their%20flaws%2C%20they%20at%20least%20had%20the%20humility%20to%20accept%20their%20failures.%20Following%20a%20deadly%20Naxal%20attack%20in%202010%2C%20P.%20Chidambaram%20repeatedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchidambaram-buck-stops-with-me-take-full-responsibility-414884%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20buck%20stops%20at%20my%20desk%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20the%20incumbent%20home%20minister%20ever%20say%20so%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Manipur%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFreelancers%20versus%20established%20houses%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20of%20those%20opposing%20the%20list%20have%20asked%20for%20calling%20out%20the%20bad%20names.%20They%20can%20look%20within.%20How%20many%20stories%20have%20they%20done%20to%20call%20out%20the%20%E2%80%98journalism%E2%80%99%20of%20these%2014%20or%20countless%20similar%20names%20or%20their%20media%20houses%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20duty%20to%20expose%20the%20hateful%20agenda%20of%20these%20media%20houses%20is%20largely%20fulfilled%20by%20new%20fact-checkers%2C%20whom%20the%20established%20names%20are%20not%20even%20comfortable%20admitting%20into%20their%20pantheon%20of%20journalists.%20There%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20fact-checking%20organisations%20comprising%20a%20handful%20of%20young%20people%2C%20had%20the%20bigger%20institutions%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVeterans%20often%20express%20the%20need%20to%20cleanse%20the%20media.%20But%20who%20will%20do%20it%2C%20if%20not%20they%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20column%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20at%20all%20argue%20that%20all%20those%20who%20oppose%20the%20list%20are%20either%20complicit%20with%20the%20government%20or%20have%20been%20cowed%20down.%20But%20a%20division%20between%20two%20broad%20sections%20in%20Indian%20media%20is%20discernible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20Call%20for%20Boycott%20of%20Newspapers%20Spreading%20Hatred%20Resonates%20With%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20accepted%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20believe%20grudgingly%2C%20restrictions%20on%20their%20pen%20in%20order%20to%20adjust%20themselves%20to%20the%20present%20political%20climate%2C%20and%20hence%20will%20ask%20fewer%20questions%20and%20avoid%20naming%20or%20targeting%20certain%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20others%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20any%20such%20restrictions%20that%20dilute%20their%20press%20freedom%20under%20Article%2019%20of%20the%20constitution.%20To%20know%20more%20about%20the%20adjustments%2C%20just%20check%20their%20journalism%20record%20before%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20comprises%20mostly%20established%20institutions%20with%20honourable%20bylines%20and%20impeccable%20editorial%20expertise%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20are%20mostly%20those%20with%20limited%20resources%20but%20who%20have%20done%20exemplary%20work%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20raise%20a%20question%20for%20the%20former%3A%20why%20is%20it%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20investigations%20concerning%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20spanning%20from%20coal%20deals%20and%20Adani%20to%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20hate%20speech%2C%20have%20originated%20from%20freelancers%20or%20organizations%20with%20limited%20budgets%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20tragedy%20of%20Indian%20journalism%20that%20most%20of%20these%20freelancers%20have%20a%20body%20of%20work%20behind%20them%2C%20but%20they%20find%20themselves%20not%20merely%20unemployed%2C%20but%20unemployable%20under%20the%20present%20political%20climate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%2080%25%20of%20those%20working%20in%20the%20media%20and%20publishing%20industry%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%20in%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Findia%2Falmost-78-per-cent-jobs-lost-in-media-and-publishing-industry-in-5-years-cmie-survey%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy.%C2%A0The%20industry%20employed%20over%2010.3%20lakh%20people%20in%20September%202016%2C%20which%20came%20down%20to%20a%20mere%202.3%20lakh%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20now%20has%20fewer%20journalists%20to%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable.%20Unemployment%20in%20the%20media%20sector%20dilutes%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20and%20damages%20electoral%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20list%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cleanse%20one%E2%80%99s%20home%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20list%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20journalism%20stands%20threatened%20because%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20media%20community%20has%20chosen%20to%20shelve%20their%20quiver%2C%20and%20opted%20to%20adjust%20and%20accommodate.%20Personally%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20list%2C%20but%20I%20am%20prepared%20to%20understand%20the%20exceptional%20circumstances%20under%20which%20it%20has%20arrived.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20opposing%20the%20list%20should%20ask%3A%20Was%20there%20any%20option%20left%20with%20INDIA%3F%20Why%20did%20the%20great%20names%20of%20Indian%20media%20allow%20such%20%E2%80%98journalism%E2%80%99%20to%20go%20uncontested%3F%20What%20stopped%20them%20from%20investing%20their%20resources%20into%20uncovering%20these%20hateful%20newsrooms%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20section%20of%20the%20Indian%20media%20failed%20to%20keep%20its%20house%20in%20order%20and%20succumbed%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20The%20opposition%20alliance%20has%20shown%20us%20our%20compromised%20and%20distorted%20face.%20Instead%20of%20grandstanding%2C%20take%20it%20as%20a%20reality%20check%2C%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cleanse%20our%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fashutosh-bhardwaj%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAshutosh%20Bhardwaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20the%20award-winning%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Femail.mg1.substack.com%2Fc%2FeJwlkF1urDAMhVczeQOFhAR4yMPVHXUDXQAyiWdICwElTildfUNHso5k-efYnwXC5xZPs2-J2CUjnTuagEdakAgjywnj6J2RXDRatoI5wzthu4n5ND4i4gp-MWzP0-ItkN_C1d1wpQbJZqOsAC2tVuAGK4UFpSROgiPnzrqhf5lCdh6DRbOF5Rx38I4tZiba003-u4m3Esdx1LDCzxZqH0p-R6C5erfR71TdI8KaqjsuOZULUvV_y4HiWfrcXmSQSqqu50PLvBHlk0aIvimqulrU_WPqpxbxoZ0EgVM9fLchzH24tXx9NnXKUyKwn7XdVhbNB8wBvnwp0oyHj1gOuv4fS3nNwdM5YoBpQWcoZmT0ovsHanxiwFiouxHINLrluh-GnmupXiQK