nt%20but%20also%20a%20path%20paved%20for%20future%20generations%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20on%20her%20role%20brimming%20with%20responsibilities%2C%20Sonali%20Ghosh%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20joy%20while%20working%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59731%2Ftirthan-valley-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20nature%E2%80%99s%20paradise%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20takes%20us%20on%20a%20journey%20through%20her%20experiences%2C%20sharing%20both%20her%20challenges%20and%20offering%20a%20glimpse%20into%20a%20day%20in%20the%20life%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F13673%2Fbenefits-of-flood-kaziranga-national-park-assam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaziranga%20National%20Park%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fa%3Efield%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20her%20calling%20in%20nature%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Pune%20in%201975%2C%20Sonali%20had%20a%20childhood%20that%20consisted%20of%20travelling%20and%20moving%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20in%20a%20middle-class%20Bengali%20%3Cem%3Eprobashi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(non-resident)%20family.%20My%20father%E2%80%99s%20army%20background%20allowed%20us%20to%20move%20constantly.%20While%20it%20might%20sound%20hectic%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20new%20people%20and%20know%20their%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20nature%20which%20allowed%20me%20to%20have%20a%20connection%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20herself%20a%20%E2%80%9Clate%20bloomer%E2%80%9D%2C%20Sonali%20notes%20that%20she%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20Biology%20when%20she