gation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20has%20released%20pictures%20of%2010%20Khalistan%20supporters%20who%20were%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20the%20United%20States%20came%20under%20attack%20twice%20this%20year%2C%20first%20in%20March%20and%20then%20again%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeeking%20the%20help%20of%20the%20general%20public%20in%20nabbing%20them%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20issued%20three%20separate%20%E2%80%98request%20for%20identification%20and%20information%E2%80%99%20notices%20against%20the%20accused%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fnia-seeks-information-about-10-accused-in-attack-on-indian-consulate-in-san-francisco%2Fcid%2F1967879%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20agency%20has%20sought%20information%20of%20importance%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20their%20arrest%20or%20apprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20two%20notices%20carry%20photographs%20of%20two%20accused%20each%2C%20the%20third%20notice%20shows%20pictures%20of%20the%20other%20six%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20agency%20assured%20people%20that%20it%20would%20not%20reveal%20the%20identity%20of%20anyone%20sharing%20information%20about%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20attack%2C%20which%20took%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20March%2018%20and%2019%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20allegedly%20by%20some%20Khalistani%20supporters%2C%20who%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20consulate%20premises%20and%20attempted%20to%20set%20it%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%2C%20some%20%E2%80%9Cslogan-shouting%20Khalistani%20supporters%E2%80%9D%20broke%20the%20makeshift%20security%20barriers%20put%20up%20by%20the%20San%20Francisco%20police%20and%20put%20up%20two%20%E2%80%9Cso-called%20Khalistani%20flags%20on%20the%20consulate%20premises%E2%80%9D%2C%20whilst%20damaging%20the%20consulate%20building%2C%20assaulting%20and%20causing%20injuries%20to%20the%20consulate%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20consulate%20again%20came%20under%20attack%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20July%201%20and%202%2C%20again%20allegedly%20by%20Khalistan%20supporters%20who%20tried%20to%20burn%20down%20the%20consulate.%C2%A0The%20local%20fire%20department%20put%20out%20the%20fire%20and%20no%20major%20damages%20or%20injuries%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20video%20uploaded%20to%20Twitter%20by%20Khalistan%20supporters%20themselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fkhalistan-nijjar-san-francisco-indian-consulate-arson%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20act%20of%20arson%20took%20place%20on%20July%201-2.%C2%A0The%20video%2C%20as%20PTI%20had%20reported%2C%20had%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cviolence%20begets%20violence%E2%80%9D%20over%20it.%20It%20also%20showed%20news%20articles%20related%20to%20the%20death%20of%20Canada-based%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%20chief%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%20by%20unidentified%20masked%20men%20on%20June%2019%20when%20he%20was%20leaving%20the%20Guru%20Nanak%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20Vancouver.%20He%20was%20a%20declared%20terrorist%20in%20India%2C%20wanted%20in%20several%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20allegation%20by%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20stating%20that%20Canada%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%E2%80%9D%20evidence%20that%20there%20is%20a%20possible%20Indian%20link%20in%20the%20assassination%20has%20once%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20and%20the%20support%20for%20the%20separatist%20Khalistan%20movement%20outside%20India.%20With%20his%20statement%2C%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20relations%20have%20reached%20their%20lowest%20ebb.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20attack%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20the%20