%22Decoding%20the%20New%20Ways%20to%20Understand%20the%20Enigma%20That%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21153304%2FF6hvYDgWIAAsrYc.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20book%20reviews%20often%20start%20or%20conclude%20by%20stating%20what%20they%20think%20is%20absent%20or%20lacking%20in%20the%20book.%20Here%20the%20author%2C%20a%20journalist%20of%20long%20standing%2C%20whose%20first%20book%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwatch-deve-gowda-did-not-receive-his-due-because-of-caste-language-and-geographical-disadvantages%5C%22%3Ebiography%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%20%E2%80%93%20was%20widely%20appreciated%20for%20shedding%20first%20light%20on%20several%20facets%20of%20this%20largely%20little-written%20about%20Indian%20premier%2C%20starts%20his%20new%20book%20by%20stating%20what%20it%20is%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20first%20sentence%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Introduction%E2%80%99%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3EStrange%20Burdens%3A%20The%20Politics%20and%20Predicaments%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Ecould%20not%20have%20been%20straighter%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20book%20is%20not%20a%20biography%E2%80%9D.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20paragraphs%2C%20Sugata%20Srinivasaraju%20states%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20book%20is%20not%20to%20assess%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20failures%20and%20successes%20and%20juxtapose%20them%20in%20tabular%20form.%20He%20also%20does%20not%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9Cseek%20to%20answer%20questions%20of%20(Gandhi%E2%80%99s)%20suitability%20or%20unsuitability%20for%20a%20public%20role.%E2%80%9D%20The%20book%20is%20also%20not%20%E2%80%9Can%20excavation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20subject%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life.%20Finally%2C%20the%20author%20states%20that%20this%20book%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmyth-busting%20or%20myth-making%20exercise%20nor%20is%20it%20an%20inquisition.%E2%80%9D%20The%20downside%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20that%20there%20is%20little%20new%20information%20about%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20331px)%2085vw%2C%20331px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21152711%2F81tAQGgv-uL._SL1500_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22331%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21152711%2F81tAQGgv-uL._SL1500_.jpg%20765w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21152711%2F81tAQGgv-uL._SL1500_-191x300.jpg%20191w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21152711%2F81tAQGgv-uL._SL1500_-653x1024.jpg%20653w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674111%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22519%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESugata%20Srinivasaraju%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EStrange%20Burdens%3A%20The%20Politics%20and%20Predicaments%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EVintage%20Books%20(August%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20then%20is%20this%20book%20in%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20words%20and%20does%20the%20book%20succeed%20in%20achieving%20its%20purpose%3F%20The%20latter%20part%20of%20the%20question%20shall%20be%20taken%20up%20later%2C%20but%20let%20us%20first%20list%20out%20what%20the%20author%20has%20attempted%20to%20do.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20Srinivasaraju%20is%20conscious%20that%20previous%20efforts%20at%20writings%20on%20his%20subject%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20run%20down%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20or%20%E2%80%9Csimply%20celebrate%20him.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20most%20Indian%20biographies%20or%20books%20in%20the%20genre%20that%20the%20author%20chose%20tended%20to%20be%20hagiographies%20or%20sympathetic%20accounts.%20There%20are%20few%20works%20that%20appreciate%20the%20subject%E2%80%99s%20positives%20and%20critically%20view%20only%20the%20negatives.%20I%20was%20aware%20of%20what%20Srinivasaraju%20terms%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbinary%20pitfall%E2%80%9D%20while%20working%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20on%20the%20biography%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20polarising%20leader%20to%20date%3A%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20certainly%20is%20the%20second%20most%20popular%20leader%20in%20India%20today%20and%20probably%20the%20second%20most%20polarising%20too%20%E2%80%93%20but%20for%20reasons%20markedly%20different%20from%20the%20Indian%20premier.%20Being%20aware%20of%20the%20need%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20path%20of%20neutrality%2C%20the%20author%20successfully%20creates%20a%20space%20for%20himself%20between%20the%20two%20pathways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20is%20true%20to%20the%20stated%20objective%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpursuit%20of%20political%20insight%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20an%20analysis%20of%20different%20%E2%80%98verticals%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20his%20political%20career%20are%20scrutinised%20by%20the%20author.%20He%20also%20examines%20various%20circumstances%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20how%20he%20navigated%20through%20these%20channels.%20The%20book%20provides%20detailed%20accounts%20of%20the%20subject%E2%80%99s%20thoughts%20and%20views%20on%20important%20issues%20and%20developments.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20author%20painstakingly%20researches%20and%20cites%20available%20sources%20%E2%80%93%20interviews%2C%20speeches%2C%20commentaries%20and%20other%20published%20material%20that%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20this%20approach%2C%20information%20and%20opinions%20that%20lie%20scattered%20get%20collated%20in%20a%20single%20text%20with%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20perspective.%20On%20the%20personal%20side%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20Srinivasaraju%20is%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20tragically%20disrupted%20by%20the%20violent%20deaths%20of%20the%20two%20people%20to%20whom%20he%20was%20extremely%20close%20%E2%80%93%20grandmother%20Indira%20and%20father%20Rajiv.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20his%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20a%20life%20like%20no%20other%20in%20Indian%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivasaraju%20does%20not%20stick%20to%20mere%20narration%20%E2%80%93%20for%20everyone%20knows%20that%20Gandhi%20was%20hurtled%20into%20a%20pit%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20grief%20when%20still%20in%20his%20teens.%20There%20is%20a%20poignant%20narrative%20section%20of%20the%20young%20lad%20discovering%20that%20the%20two%20policemen%2C%20who%20taught%20him%20how%20to%20play%20badminton%2C%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20assassinated%20his%20grandmother.%20The%20author%20goes%20beyond%20this%20and%20jumps%20to%20the%20awkward%20silence%20for%20which%20even%20the%20interviewer%2C%20historian%20Shruti%20Kapila%20appeared%20somewhat%20repentant%20for%20having%20asked%20a%20question%20about%20how%20he%20processed%20the%20violence%20in%20his%20life%2C%20during%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df4H6tIJp6Zc%5C%22%3E2022%20interaction%20in%20Cambridge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20author%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20even%20a%20few%20decades%20later%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstill%20struggling%20to%20negotiate%20his%20grief%20and%20the%20labyrinthine%20emotional%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20anguish%2C%20says%20the%20book%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20tragedy%20that%20shook%20his%20core%20in%201984%20and%20again%20seven%20years%20later%20in%20May%201991%20when%20a%20suicide%20bomber%20sneaked%20close%20enough%20to%20blow%20his%20father%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20into%20smithereens%2C%20has%20always%20remained%20personal.%20He%20never%20embarked%20on%20avenging%20it%20either%20personally%20or%20by%20calling%20upon%20people%20to%20do%20so.%20In%20contrast%2C%20revenge%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Hindu%20rightwing%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20time%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20till%20date.%20Nathuram%20Godse%20viewed%20his%20act%20as%20a%20form%20of%20reprisal%20or%20retaliatory%20act%20for%20the%20values%20that%20Gandhi%20expounded%20and%20for%20the%20politics%20he%20pursued.%20Even%20today%2C%20hardly%20a%20day%20goes%20by%20without%20someone%20from%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20making%20a%20call%20to%20seek%20revenge%2C%20for%20what%20%E2%80%98is%20being%20done%E2%80%99%20in%20some%20part%20of%20India%2C%20or%20for%20what%20happened%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20moment%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20a%20thought%20%E2%80%93%20what%20kind%20of%20a%20man%20would%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20been%20if%20he%20too%20was%20driven%20by%20feeling%20of%20revenge%20or%20if%20he%20was%20as%20ruthless%20as%2C%20say%20Modi%3F%20Because%20negotiating%20grief%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20public%20life%20of%20the%20surviving%20three%20Gandhis%20in%20the%20Congress.%20The%20author%20digs%20out%20old%20forgotten%20shreds%20of%20emotional%20exchanges.%20Particular%20poignant%20are%20details%20of%20Priyanka%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20with%20Nalini%20Sriharan%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20letters%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20assassin%20besides%20those%20to%20V.%20Mohini%20Giri%2C%20then%20the%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivasaraju%20does%20not%20go%20beyond%20the%20standard%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20said%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20actually%20her%20children%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20No%20bones%20about%20that%2C%20because%20some%20matters%20are%20too%20personal%20and%20increasingly%20not%20being%20put%20on%20record%20by%20leaders%20at%20any%20place.%20For%20instance%2C%20what%20details%20beyond%20what%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20would%20historians%20and%20analysts%20of%20the%20future%20find%20on%20Modi%3F%20Would%20they%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20fathom%20what%20thoughts%20or%20considerations%20went%20through%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20mind%20before%20he%20went%20on%20air%20to%20announce%20demonetisation%20in%20November%202016%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELikewise%2C%20till%20the%20time%20any%20of%20the%20three%20Gandhis%20write%20their%20own%20memoirs%20of%20those%20days%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98true%E2%80%99%20story%20will%20never%20be%20known.%20But%20if%20what%20Srinivasaraju%20writes%20is%20actually%20correct%2C%20can%20one%20presume%20that%20neither%20Rahul%20nor%20Priyanka%20would%20ever%20become%20the%20premier%20even%20if%20opportunity%20knocks%20on%20their%20doors%3F%20If%20this%20answer%20is%20in%20the%20affirmative%2C%20it%20would%20considerably%20alter%20equations%20in%20the%20opposition%20space%20either%20before%202024%20or%20till%20the%20time%20Modi%2C%20or%20any%20other%20BJP%20leader%2C%20is%20in%20office.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20view%20of%20political%20power%20is%20important%20because%20at%20another%20place%2C%20the%20author%20points%20out%20that%20he%20said%20at%20one%20point%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20never%20interested%20him%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpart%20of%20it%20also%20perhaps%20meant%20that%20he%20did%20not%20really%20understand%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20analyses%20Gandhi%20from%20four%20different%20facets%20%E2%80%93%20the%20privilege%20into%20which%20he%20was%20born%20and%20from%20which%20he%20could%20never%20escape%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20two%20assassinations%20that%20punctuated%20his%20life%20before%20he%20matured%20as%20an%20independently%20thinking%20adult%3B%20the%20ideological%20%E2%80%98rigidity%E2%80%99%20which%20many%20%E2%80%93%20including%20this%20reviewer%20%E2%80%93%20would%20term%2C%20%E2%80%98steadfastness%E2%80%99%2C%20after%20years%20of%20dithering%20on%20taking%20a%20stand%20on%20resolute%20secularism%3B%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20idealism%20and%20his%20constant%20search%20for%20political%20utopia%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20what%20Srinivasaraju%20terms%20the%20%E2%80%98conservative%20project%E2%80%99.%20While%20the%20first%20three%20facets%20are%20self-explanatory%2C%20the%20fourth%20is%20somewhat%20muddled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20is%20now%20attempting%20to%20reclaim%20and%20restore%20the%20vocabulary%20of%20the%20lost%20liberal%20era%2C%20says%20Srinivsaraju.%20Gandhi%20is%20presenting%20the%20past%20as%20perfect%2C%20whereas%20it%20was%20not%20always%20unwavering%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20late%201960s.%20The%20hazard%20of%20writing%20about%20someone%20who%20is%20evolving%20by%20the%20day%20and%20when%20the%20political%20narrative%20is%20swiftly%20changing%20is%20that%20several%20suppositions%2C%20observations%20and%20conclusions%20would%20change%20with%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20political%20discourse.%20For%20instance%2C%20would%2C%20between%20now%20and%20the%20next%20elections%2C%20Gandhi%20continue%20to%20speak%20about%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20the%20way%20he%20did%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3F%20If%20he%20does%20not%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20is%20likely%20after%20the%20words%20of%20caution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsavarkar-our-god-uddhav-thackeray-warns-rahul-gandhi-over-his-remark-3895605%5C%22%3Efollowing%20his%20last%20tirade%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20would%20Gandhi%20still%20be%20considered%20ideologically%20firm%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20that%20Srinivasaraju%20is%20not%20sympathetic%20towards%20Gandhi%2C%20especially%20when%20there%20is%20need.%20For%20instance%2C%20while%20writing%20on%20the%20hostilities%20he%20has%20faced%2C%20the%20book%20notes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cto%20criticize%20(Rahul%20Gandhi)%20became%20a%20parasitic%20industry%20that%20the%20BJP%20heavily%20invested%20in.%E2%80%9D%20But%20there%20are%20errors%20and%20na%C3%AFvet%C3%A9%20that%20the%20author%20points%20to.%20Top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20immature%20actions%20is%20undoubtedly%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frahul-gandhi-trashes-ordinance-shames-government%2Farticleshow%2F23180950.cms%5C%22%3Etearing%20of%20the%20ordinance%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20the%20UPA%20government%20promulgated%20to%20circumvent%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20disqualifying%20convicted%20legislators.%20In%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20mind%2C%20this%20is%20little%20but%20%E2%80%9Csheer%20impulsive%20behaviour%20and%20indiscretion.%E2%80%9D%20Ironically%2C%20it%20came%20back%20to%20haunt%20him%20in%202023%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20ordinance%20had%20become%20law%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20been%20disqualified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivasaraju%20is%20scathing%20for%20the%20showcasing%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20status%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Hindu%20caste%20heap%E2%80%9D.%20The%20author%20argues%20that%20instead%20of%20this%2C%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20team%20should%20have%20presented%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20egalitarian%20ideal%E2%80%9D.%20With%20Modi%20once%20again%20trying%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20sole%20protector%20of%20Hindu%20prestige%2C%20especially%20after%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20became%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20political%20tool%2C%20Gandhi%20and%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20shall%20be%20tempted%20to%20go%20back%20in%20time.%20Already%20there%20are%20signs%20of%20not%20entering%20into%20a%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20territory%20and%20point%20out%20that%20not%20all%20Hindus%20are%20Sanatanis.%20Although%20written%20when%20few%20could%20have%20ever%20imagined%20the%20way%20this%20controversy%20erupted%20and%20how%20the%20BJP%20will%20try%20to%20enlist%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20leaders%20could%20do%20well%20to%20deliberate%20on%20a%20suggestion%20in%20the%20book%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20strategy%20is%20not%20about%20relentlessly%20speaking%20about%20being%20a%20cultural%20Hindu%20in%20an%20academic%20language%20but%20acting%20it%20out%20in%20plebeian%20ways.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20Modi%20and%20others%20in%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20have%20succeeded.%20This%20book%20may%20not%20arm%20the%20readers%20with%20more%20%E2%80%98information%E2%80%99%20about%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20will%20surely%20arm%20them%20with%20new%20ways%20to%20comprehend%20the%20enigma%20of%20a%20public%20figure%20who%20continues%20to%20baffle%20most%20%E2%80%93%20within%20his%20party%20and%20outside.%20Whatever%20else%20it%20may%20or%20may%20not%20do%2C%20Srinivasaraju%20with%20aplomb%20establishes%20that%20his%20subject%20certainly%20is%20no%20%E2%80%98Pappu%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695295846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21153304%2FF6hvYDgWIAAsrYc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Frahul-gandhi-sugata-srinivasaraju-book-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20book%20takes%20known%20material%20and%20tries%20to%20present%20fresh%20light%20on%20the%20Congress%20party%20leader%20and%20shows%20why%20he%20is%20no%20'Pappu'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Frahul-gandhi-sugata-srinivasaraju-book-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana%2C%20Navya%20%26amp%3B%20Ananya%20come%20together%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695294797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103837800%2Cimgsize-53872.cms%