0clear%20signs%20of%20weakness%20in%20the%20housing%20market%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbank-of-england-halts-run-of-interest-rate-hikes-as-economy-slows-123092100783_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fbank-of-england-halts-run-of-interest-rate-hikes-as-economy-slows-123092100783_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fbank-of-england-halts-run-of-interest-rate-hikes-as-economy-slows-123092100783_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Banking%20Liquidity%20Deficit%20Jumps%20to%20Over%204-Year%20High%20at%20Rs%201.46%20Lakh%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FRBI_0_1_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20banking%20liquidity%20deficit%20has%20jumped%20to%20over%20a%20four-year%20high%20at%20Rs%201.46%20lakh%20crore%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2020%2C%20on%20account%20of%20outflows%20related%20to%20advance%20tax%20payments%20and%20preparation%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20collection%2C%20which%20is%20a%20quarterly%20phenomenon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Findia-markets-liquidity%2Findias-banking-system-liquidity-deficit-jumps-to-over-4-year-high-idUSKBN30Q0BQ%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20this%20is%20the%20highest%20single%20day%20shortfall%20since%20April%2023%2C%202019.%20And%20banking%20system%20liquidity%20had%20slipped%20into%20deficit%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20fiscal%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Fbanking%2Findias-banking-system-liquidity-slips-into-deficit-first-time-in-fy24%2Farticleshow%2F102927825.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20August%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20comes%20after%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20ordered%20banks%20to%20set%20aside%2010%25%20of%20their%20incremental%20deposits%20%E2%80%93%20as%20incremental%20cash%20reserve%20ratio%20(ICRR)%20%E2%80%93%20received%20between%20May%2019%20and%20July%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiquidity%20deficit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20liquidity%20means%20how%20much%20cash%20is%20readily%20available%2C%20or%20how%20quickly%20you%20can%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20your%20cash.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20five-year%20fixed%20deposit%E2%80%99s%20liquidity%20is%20lower%20than%20a%20savings%20account.%20But%20you%20can%20take%20cash%20out%20whenever%20you%20need%20from%20your%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELiquidity%20in%20the%20banking%20system%20means%20how%20much%20cash%20is%20readily%20available%20with%20the%20banks%20to%20meet%20their%20short-term%20business%20and%20financial%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20any%20given%20day%2C%20if%20the%20banking%20system%20is%20a%20net%20borrower%20from%20the%20RBI%20under%20Liquidity%20Adjustment%20Facility%20(LAF)%2C%20the%20system%20liquidity%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20in%20deficit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%20if%20the%20banking%20system%20is%20a%20net%20lender%20to%20the%20RBI%2C%20the%20system%20liquidity%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20in%20surplus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20LAF%20is%20a%20tool%20used%20in%20monetary%20policy%2C%20primarily%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20that%20allows%20banks%20to%20borrow%20money%20through%20repurchase%20agreements%20(repos)%20or%20to%20make%20loans%20to%20the%20RBI%20through%20reverse%20repo%20agreements.%20This%20maintains%20the%20liquidity%20pressures%20in%20the%20financial%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20there%E2%80%99s%20another%20distinct%20tool%20used%20by%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20manage%20liquidity%20in%20the%20banking%20system.%20Both%20the%20tools%20serve%20different%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20LAF%20is%20used%20for%20routine%20liquidity%20management%2C%20Marginal%20Standing%20Facility%20(MSF)%20is%20meant%20for%20extraordinary%20situations%20when%20banks%20need%20funds%20urgently.%20The%20interest%20rates%20for%20MSF%20are%20higher%2C%20making%20it%20a%20costlier%20source%20of%20funds%20for%20banks%20compared%20to%20the%20LAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20banks%20borrowed%20a%20record%20Rs%201.97%20lakh%20crore%20under%20the%20MSF%20and%20parked%20around%20Rs%2046%2C724%20crore%20under%20a%20special%20deposit%20facility%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fliquidity-deficit-in-banks-hits-1-5l-crore%2Farticleshow%2F103823087.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ethe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20aggregate%20outflows%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202.50%20lakh%20crore%20is%20expected%2C%20because%20the%20twin%20outflows%20(advance%20tax%20payments%20and%20outflows%20towards%20GST)%20have%20occurred%20in%20the%20same%20reporting%20fortnight%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20bankers%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20has%20happened%20at%20a%20time%20when%20a%20chunk%20of%20the%20money%20is%20not%20available%20for%20use%20as%20it%20is%20blocked%20in%20the%20incremental%20cash%20reserve%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20%E2%80%9Canother%20drain%20on%20rupee%20liquidity%20could%20be%20from%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20FX%20intervention%20if%20depreciation%20pressures%20on%20the%20rupee%20persist%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaura%20Sen%20Gupta%2C%20an%20economist%20with%20IDFC%20First%20Bank%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETraders%20told%20Reuters%20that%20the%20winding%20down%20the%20I-CRR%2C%20which%20was%20imposed%20on%20banks%20in%20August%2C%20is%20adding%20to%20the%20liquidity%20tightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpasna%20Bhardwaj%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20the%20RBI%20is%20expected%20to%20keep%20liquidity%20tight%20in%20the%20near%20term%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20short-term%20rates%20elevated%2C%20given%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20rupee%20and%20underlying%20inflationary%20risks%2C%20which%20may%20also%20prevent%20the%20central%20bank%20from%20announcing%20variable%20repo%20rate%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20liquidity%20deficit%20will%2C%20narrow%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695294057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FRBI_0_1_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0_0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Findias-banking-liquidity-deficit-jumps-to-over-4-year-high-at-rs-1-46-lakh-crore%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20happened%20due%20to%20the%20account%20of%20outflows%20related%20to%20advance%20tax%20payments%20and%20preparation%20for%20GST%20collection%2C%20which%20is%20a%20quarterly%20phenomenon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Findias-banking-liquidity-deficit-jumps-to-over-4-year-high-at-rs-1-46-lakh-crore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20wishes%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20'Dhoom%204'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695293306000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-103837376%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-57764%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2F