20luggage%20or%20vehicle%20covers%20with.%20It%20is%20thick%20and%20heavy.%20In%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20hot%20and%20humid%20climate%2C%20we%20end%20up%20profusely%20sweating%20and%20they%20are%20not%20fit%20for%20the%20long%20hours%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20under%20the%20sun.%20I%20wore%20it%20on%20Monday%20but%20I%20refuse%20to%20wear%20it%20now.%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20give%20a%20written%20explanation%20but%20since%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20abandoning%20it%2C%20my%20seniors%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20press%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20security%20wing%20staffer%20posted%20at%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20the%20old%20parliament%20building%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20earlier%2C%20the%20government%20this%20time%20around%20gave%20stitched%20uniforms%20to%20staffers%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20them%20getting%20uniforms%20which%20do%20not%20fit%20them.%20So%20far%2C%20each%20staffer%20received%20around%20Rs%2013%2C000%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20a%20year%20as%20allowance%20year%20for%20uniforms%20depending%20upon%20their%20grade%20and%20entitlement.%20They%20purchased%20and%20got%20their%20own%20uniform%20stitched%20based%20on%20the%20sanctioned%20design.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20the%20amount%20which%20was%20to%20be%20credited%20to%20their%20accounts%20by%20April%20was%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20allowance%2C%20we%20will%20be%20given%20new%20uniforms.%20The%20uniforms%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20stitched%20to%20our%20measurements.%20We%20have%20to%20wear%20the%20sizes%20that%20are%20available.%20Some%20of%20us%20got%20the%20uniform%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20boots%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOthers%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20design%20of%20the%20new%20outfit%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20new%20uniform%20does%20not%20go%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20parliament%2C%20for%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20combat%20outfit%20worn%20by%20armed%20forces.%20They%20said%20parliament%20security%20staff%20fall%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20civilian%20staff%2C%20for%20their%20role%20is%20limited%20to%20facilitate%20MPs%20at%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20officials%20even%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20uniform%20is%20what%20usually%20armed%20forces%20wear%20during%20combat.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20eerily%20looks%20like%20the%20uniform%20worn%20by%20Pakistani%20Rangers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20news%20of%20new%20uniforms%20for%20parliament%20staffers%20has%20been%20around%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20launched%20criticism%20against%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20just%20reducing%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20showpieces%20to%20please%20the%20ruler%2C%20this%20government%20has%20also%20cut%2025%2C000%20from%20each%20of%20the%20600%20Parliament%20security%20staff%20for%20this%20uniform.%20Why%20should%20our%20security%20personnel%20suffer%20for%20the%20Rule%E2%80%99s%20fancy%20dress%20competition%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20Congress%20whip%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENot%20just%20reducing%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20showpieces%20to%20please%20the%20Ruler%2C%20this%20Govt%20has%20also%20cut%2025%2C000%20from%20each%20of%20the%20600%20Parliament%20Security%20staff%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98uniform%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20should%20our%20security%20personnel%20suffer%20for%20the%20Ruler%E2%80%99s%20fancy%20dress%20competition%20%3F%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FParliamentBuilding%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ParliamentBuilding%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fsc3MBPmzxg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fsc3MBPmzxg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manickam%20Tagore%20.B%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%E2%9C%8B%E0%AE%AE%E0%AE%BE%E