%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F10140122%2Fmahesh-raut_facebook.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Five%20years%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmahesh-raut-forest-rights-bhima-koregon%5C%22%3E36-year-old%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20Mahesh%20Raut%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20arrested%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20September%2021%2C%20granted%20him%20bail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20which%20is%20handling%20the%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%2C%20sought%20two%20weeks%E2%80%99%20time%20to%20appeal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20HC%2C%20however%2C%20granted%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20A.S.%20Gadkari%20and%20Sharmila%20Deshmukh%20granted%20him%20bail.%20The%20court%20has%20expressed%20the%20view%20that%20many%20sections%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20applied%20against%20Raut%20were%20not%20tenable.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20also%20took%20his%20long%20incarceration%20into%20consideration%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Raut%20has%20no%20criminal%20antecedents%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20granted%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaut%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20five%20persons%20to%20be%20arrested%20on%20June%206%2C%202018%2C%20has%20already%20spent%201%2C930%20days%20in%20jail.%20He%20becomes%20the%20sixth%20person%20out%20of%2016%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20to%20have%20been%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%2C%20first%20handled%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%2C%20Raut%20was%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfunding%E2%80%9D%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20event%20organised%20on%20December%2031%2C%202017%20in%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Shaniwarwada%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20Brahmin%20hub%20%E2%80%93%20and%20which%20according%20to%20the%20state%20police%20had%20triggered%20violence%20a%20day%20later%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon%2C%2030%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Pune.%20Taking%20over%20from%20the%20Pune%20police%2C%20the%20NIA%20had%20simply%20replicated%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20allegations%20against%20Raut%20were%20entirely%20based%20on%20letters%20allegedly%20procured%20from%20the%20laptop%20of%20his%20co-accused%20%E2%80%93%20Surendra%20Gadling%20and%20Rona%20Wilson.%20In%20this%20letter%2C%20the%20agency%20claims%20a%20man%20named%20Mahesh%20had%20allegedly%20paid%20%E2%80%9C5L%E2%80%9D%20to%20organise%20the%20event.%20There%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20substantiate%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20letter%20or%20that%20the%20said%20Mahesh%20mentioned%20in%20the%20letter%20is%20really%20Raut.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20high%20court%20termed%20the%20letter%20as%20%E2%80%9Chearsay%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20that%20cannot%20be%20relied%20upon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20relying%20on%20the%20recent%20bail%20order%20passed%20in%20Raut%E2%80%99s%20co-accused%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%20and%20Arun%20Ferriera%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20observed%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20documents%20have%20not%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20appellant%20(Raut)%20and%20therefore%2C%20as%20has%20held%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Vernon%20(supra)%20these%20communications%20or%20contents%20thereof%20have%20weak%20probative%20value%20or%20quality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20another%20claim%20by%20the%20NIA%20that%20one%20Com.%20Prakash%20claimed%20to%20have%20handed%20over%20some%20money%20to%20Ray%2C%20the%20order%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAssu%3Cspan%3Emi%3Cspan%3Eng%20fo%3Cspan%3Er%20the%20sa%3Cspan%3Eke%20of%20arguments%2C%20Co%3Cspan%3Em.%20Prakash%20had%20handed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eover%20Rs.%20Five%20Lakhs%20to%20the%20Appellant%20for%20its%20onward%20transmission%20or%20handing%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eover%20to%20Com.%20Surendra%20and%20Com.%20Sudhir%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20corroboration%20at%20all%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20it%2C%20that%20the%20Appellant%20in%20fact%20received%20the%20money%20and%20handed%20it%20over%20to%20co-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccused.%20Merely%20because%20Com.%20Prakash%20says%20that%20he%20handed%20over%20the%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eamount%20to%20Appellant%2C%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Eipso-facto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0does%20not%20make%20Appellant%20recipient%20of%20it%2C%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20want%20of%20basic%20corroboration%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F672697012%2FMahesh-Raut-bail-order%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Mahesh%20Raut%20bail%20order%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EMahesh%20Raut%20bail%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F672697012%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-zp9KD6XGttqtvT3ndn5J%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7080062794348508%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Mahesh%20Raut%20bail%20order%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%2019%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20has%20been%20produced%20on%20record%20showing%20that%20people%20had%20been%20recruited%20or%20joined%20the%20banned%20organisation%20%5BCPI%20(Maoist)%5D%20through%20Raut.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6therefore%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20%3Cem%3Eprima-facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20accept%20the%20contention%20of%20Respondent-NIA%20that%2C%20the%20Appellant%20has%20committed%20the%20offence%20relating%20to%20recruitment%20of%20persons%20into%20the%20said%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20Raut%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Mihir%20Desai%20had%20represented%20academic%20and%20civil%20liberties%20activist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbombay-hc-anand-teltumbde-bail%5C%22%3EAnand%20Teltumbde%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20case.%20Raut%E2%80%99s%20case%20too%20was%20largely%20argued%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20parity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDesai%20submitted%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20Raut%20are%20three-fold%3A%20(i)%20membership%20of%20a%20banned%20organization%2C%20(ii)%20given%20the%20task%20of%20recruiting%20persons%20to%20the%20said%20organisation%20and%20(iii)%20handling%20of%20funds%20of%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDesai%20argued%20that%20his%20client%20was%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20outfit%20as%20claimed%20by%20NIA.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditional%20solicitor%20general%20of%20India%20Devang%20Vyas%2C%20representing%20the%20NIA%2C%20countered%20Desai%20and%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20material%20relied%20upon%20by%20the%20NIA%20clearly%20indicates%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20banned%20Organization%20of%20which%20Appellant%20(Raut)%20is%20an%20active%20member%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaut%2C%20who%20completed%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%20from%20the%20coveted%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20was%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Rural%20Development%20Fellowship.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fellowship%2C%20he%20began%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20also%20his%20home%20town.%20On%20finishing%20the%20fellowship%20stint%2C%20Raut%20continued%20to%20work%20in%20the%20region%20and%20was%20vocal%20against%20the%20rampant%20mining%20and%20displacement%20of%20Adivasi%20communities%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NIA%20claims%20that%20his%20social%20work%20in%20the%20region%20was%20only%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccover%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20Naxal%20activities%20in%20the%20conflict-prone%20areas%20of%20central%20India.%20The%20chargesheet%20claims%20that%20he%20operated%20under%20a%20fake%20name%2C%20%E2%80%9CRohit%20Verma%2C%E2%80%9D%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDesai%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20no%20material%20at%20all%20on%20record%20to%20substantiate%20the%20said%20allegations%20and%20to%20indict%20him%20in%20the%20present%20crime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%20two%20of%20his%20co-accused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felgar-parishad-bail-vernon-gonsalves-arun-ferreira-supreme-court%5C%22%3EVernon%20Gonsalves%20and%20Arun%20Ferreira%20were%20released%20on%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20NIA%20claimed%20that%20Raut%2C%20along%20with%20Ferreira%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20%E2%80%9Cinfluencing%20youths%E2%80%9D%20in%20places%20like%20TISS%20and%20Mumbai%20University%20to%20join%20the%20armed%20Naxal%20movement.%20These%20allegations%20are%20entirely%20based%20on%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20and%20there%20is%20no%20other%20direct%20evidence%20to%20substantiate%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ET%3Cspan%3Ehe%20prosecution%20also%20accused%20Raut%20of%20being%20a%20member%20of%20one%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EVisthapan%20Virodhi%20Jan%20Vikas%20Andolan%E2%80%99%20(VVJVA)%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20prosecution%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfrontal%20organisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20the%20material%20on%20record%20it%20appears%20to%20us%20that%2C%20no%20covert%20or%20overt%20terrorist%20act%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20the%20Appellant%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prosecution%20had%20also%20relied%20on%20alleged%20electronic%20evidence%20gathered%20from%20the%20hard%20disk%20of%20Nirmala%20Kumari%20%40%20Narmadakka%2C%20an%20alleged%20Maoist%20leader.%20Narmadakka%20was%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20an%20IED%20blast%20in%20Jambhulkheda%20village%2C%20Kurkheda%2C%20Maharashtra%20on%20May%201%2C%202019.%20She%20was%20later%20arrested%20and%20died%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaut%20is%20one%20of%2016%20rights%20activists%2C%20scholars%20and%20lawyers%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20has%20been%20widely%20criticised%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20curb%20dissenting%20voices%2C%20instead%20of%20holding%20the%20real%20culprits%20of%20the%202018%20violence%20against%20Dalits%20in%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20responsible.%20Five%20of%20the%20accused%20%E2%80%93%20lawyer%20Sudha%20Bharadwaj%2C%20poet%20Varavara%20Rao%2C%20academic%20Teltumbe%2C%20lawyer%20Ferreira%20and%20activist%20Gonsalves%20%E2%80%93%20are%20currently%20out%20on%20bail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EFather%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20a%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20and%20Jesuit%20priest%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fremembering-stan-swamy-whose-struggle-was-driven-by-empathy-and-love%5C%22%3Epassed%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prosecution%20has%20relied%20on%20336%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20trial%2C%20however%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20commence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20Information%20from%20the%20detailed%20order%20was%20added%20to%20this%20article%20after%20it%20was%20published.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695279863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F10140122%2Fmahesh-raut_facebook.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmahesh-raut-activist-elgar-parishad-bombay-high-court-jail-nail%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2036-year-old%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20five%20persons%20to%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20controversial%20case%2C%20on%20June%206%2C%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmahesh-raut-activist-elgar-parishad-bombay-high-court-jail-nail%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Suspends%20Visa%20Services%20in%20Canada%3B%20Ottawa%20to%20'Adjust%20Staff%20Presence'%20in%20India%20After%20'Threats'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21121523%2FUntitled-design-3-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20appears%20to%20have%20suspended%20visa%20operations%20with%20Canada%20till%20an%20indefinite%20date%2C%20amidst%20a%20diplomatic%20crisis%20that%20arose%20following%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20that%20India%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Sikh%20activist.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%C2%A0High%20Commission%20of%20Canada%20said%20that%20its%20offices%20and%20those%20of%20all%20consulates%20in%20India%20are%20open%20%E2%80%93%20noting%20at%20once%20that%20social%20media%20threats%20have%20led%20it%20to%20%E2%