%20doctor%20for%20any%20fuel%20related%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%20Now%2C%20when%20Vaibav%20hops%20onto%20a%20cab%2C%20he%20leads%20the%20driver%20to%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20station%20with%20the%20least%20waiting%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nawgati%2C%20founded%20by%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%2C%20Aryan%20Sisodia%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%2C%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%20in%20India.%20Its%20B2B%20platform%20'Aaveg'%20offers%20congestion%20monitoring%20through%20technology%20for%20fuel%20stations%20while%20the%20app%20offers%20easy%20navigation%20for%20customers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330313%2Fnawgati-fuelling-management-app-innovative-startup-shark-tank-india-bits-pilani%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Royal%20Physician%20and%20Freedom%20Fighter%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Story%20Behind%20India%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Ganeshotsav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20that%20time%20of%20the%20year%20when%20houses%20across%20the%20country%20are%20adorned%20with%20flowers%20and%20festive%20lights%20to%20welcome%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295735%2Feasy-eco-friendly-home-decor-ideas-for-ganesh-chaturthi-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ganapati%20%3Cem%3EBappa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20do%20you%20know%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20how%20this%20iconic%20festival%20came%20into%20existence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20back%20about%20131%20years.%20During%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20actively%20resisting%20British%20colonial%20rule%20and%20striving%20for%20independence%2C%20Krishnajipant%20Khasgiwale%20used%20the%20festival%20to%20demonstrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201892%2C%20Pune%20resident%20Krishnajipant%20visited%20the%20Maratha-ruled%20Gwalior.%20There%2C%20he%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261898%2Findias-oldest-ganeshotsav-was-set-up-by-a-freedom-fighter-in-1892%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20public%20celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20his%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%20and%20Balasaheb%20Natu%20%E2%80%94%20back%20home%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%2C%20also%20a%20famous%20royal%20physician%20and%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20saw%20potential%20in%20this%20festival%20to%20unite%20countrymen.%20So%20he%20installed%20the%20first%20%3Cem%3Esaarvajanik%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20public%20Ganesha%20idol%20in%20his%20home%20or%20%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E%20located%20in%20an%20area%20called%20Shalukar%20Bol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20was%20unique%20as%20it%20depicted%20the%20deity%20killing%20a%20demon.%20Made%20of%20wood%20and%20bran%2C%20the%20imagery%20was%20far%20from%20the%20usual%20calm%20and%20composed%20demeanour%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261867%2Fhow-to-carve-clay-ganesh-idol-chathurthi-sustainable-hack-eco-friendly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20Lord%20Ganesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20symbolic%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20fighting%20for%20its%20freedom%20against%20the%20colonialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20gained%20more%20attention%20when%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokman