%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation%20certificate%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20IAS%20officers%20like%20Shanavas%20was%20also%20a%20big%20motivation%20for%20Nellayapan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20many%20IAS%20officers.%20They%20are%20an%20inspiration%20for%20me%20and%20I%20wish%20to%20work%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20physics%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20his%20work%20and%20efforts%20towards%20improving%20education%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Nellayapan%20was%20made%20the%20OSD%20to%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Nagaland%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20here%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one%20for%20him%2C%20he%20shares.%20He%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20He%20credits%20his%20wife%20for%20being%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20his%20success.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20is%20my%20rock.%20She%20supported%20me%20since%20the%20day%20we%20got%20married.%20She%20also%20helped%20my%20younger%20sister%20get%20married.%20Today%2C%20my%20wife%20is%20a%20successful%20executive%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nellaya