%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fauto-workers-strike-ford-gm-stellantis_n_6503860de4b005996b6d8ece%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doc%20By%20Day%2C%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20Always%3A%2010%20Phenomenal%20Clicks%20By%20a%20Heart%20Surgeon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20conservation%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20wild%2C%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%20Dr%20Ramakanta%20Panda%20and%20nature%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20A%20major%20chunk%20of%20the%20heart%20surgeon%E2%80%99s%20day%20is%20spent%20tending%20to%20patients%20at%20the%20Asian%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20he%20established%20in%202002.%20This%20leaves%20little%20time%20for%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20whenever%20he%20does%20manage%20an%20escape%20from%20his%20busy%20schedule%2C%20he%20ventures%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326801%2Fvedhapriya-ganesan-snake-rescuer-wildlife-conservationist-pet-stylist-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20camera%20and%20some%20food%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20life%20lessons%2C%20he%20says%2C%20that%20wildlife%20photography%20has%20taught%20him%20are%20patience%20(%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20once%20waited%20for%20six%20hours%20over%20two%20days%20at%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20get%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20tiger%20couple%20mating%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20honour%20for%20the%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20lessons%20that%20have%20stood%20him%20in%20good%20stead%20both%20in%20the%20wilderness%20and%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20photography%20journey%20is%20as%20compelling%20as%20his%20medical%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20trained%20under%20the%20renowned%20Dr%20Denton%20Cooley%20%E2%80%94%20famed%20for%20the%20first%20successful%20human%20heart%20transplant%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20interview%20he%20chanced%20upon%20in%20Class%209.%20Since%20then%2C%20ma