0and%20understand%20what%20farmers%20expect%20from%20them%20when%20they%20are%20posted%20in%20the%20districts.%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20the%20trainees%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20just%20100%20poultry%20hens%2C%20Ravindra%20now%20owns%201.8%20lakh%20hens%20on%20his%2050-acre%20farm%20in%20Amravati.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20his%20experiences%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F82739%2Fifarm-integrated-aquaponics-poultry-kerala-veterinary-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farmer%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20he%20managed%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20business%20at%2016%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20financial%20constraints%2C%20Ravindra%20worked%20at%20a%20chemist%E2%80%99s%20store%20that%20would%20earn%20him%20Rs%205%20per%20day.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20own%20any%20ancestral%20land.%20Our%20financial%20condition%20was%20very%20poor.%20I%20remember%20going%20to%20college%20on%20foot%20as%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20bicycle.%20I%20used%20to%20repair%20old%20torn%20clothes%20to%20wear%20to%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20his%20job%20at%20a%20chemist%E2%80%99s%20store%2C%20he%20ventured%20into%20poultry%20farming%20after%20seeing%20his%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20success%2C%20who%20owned%20a%20400-hen%20poultry%20farm.%20So%20in%201984%2C%20when%20Ravindra%20was%20just%2016%2C%20he%20started%20poultry%20farming.%20And%20to%20help%20him%20kickstart%20this%2C%20his%20father%20gave%20him%20Rs%203%2C000%20from%20his%20provident%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1-1694610799.jpg%5C%2